title: Narra
text:
Narra em i "First Class Municipality" i stap long <a href="Palawan">Palawan</a> provins, <a href="Filipin">Filipin</a>. 2010 census i rit, Narra i kisim 65,264 manmeri. Narapla long spelim nem blong Pterocarpus Indicus (Diwai blong kantri long Filipin), Em i spelim tu National Resttlement Administration. Progrem ya, i bin wokim long namba sikis mun, 18, 1954, we manmeri blong Luzon ailan husat i nogat graun i senisim ples blong en long ya. Long namba sikis mun, 21, 1969, Municiplaity of Narra i bin wokim long Presiden Ferdinand Marcos. 
Narra i kisim narapla nem "Rice Granary of Palawan" as Narra em i nambawan ples we rais i wokim long Palawan ailan. Municiplaity ya i gat "Anihan/Palay " singsing, i save kamap long namba ten mun. 
Rasa ailan i stap long Narra, we "Katala/Abukay/Kalangay" (Narra i gat planti tok ples) o Red Vented Cockatoo pisin i stap. Na tu i stap narapla abus, binatang o pisin.
Barangay (Ol hap blong Narra).
Narra i gat 23 Barangay (liklik hap)

title: Sol
text:
Sol () emi <a href="kapitol">kapitol</a> na nambawan siti bilong <a href="Saut%20Korea">Saut Korea</a>. Sol i bin kapitol bilong Korea istat long yia <a href="1394">1394</a>. Nem ofisel long Sol i Sipesol Taun bilong Sol.
Sol i gat 9 milien manmeri long em, na i gat sampela taun klostu long Sol tu. Sol na ol taun klostu long em wantaim igat 21 milien manmeri.

title: Kristen Otodos
text:
Ol Otodos, o Kristen Otodos, o Otodos Kristen ol i manmeri bilong wanpela lain bilong <a href="Kristen">Kristen</a>. Ol Kristen ol i manmeri ol i lotuim <a href="Jisas">Jisas</a>, o Krais(t), na ol i ting olsem Jisas em i <a href="Got">Got</a> i kam long Graun. Insait long Kristen, i gat kainkain lain. Ol Otodos i lain i ting olsem bikpela bos bilong <a href="Sios">Sios</a> em i Krais, na Sios em i olsem bodi bilong Krais.
I gat samting olsem 300 milion man o meri ol i kolim yet Kristen Otodos long Graun. Planti Kristen Otodos ol i stap long <a href="Rusia">Rusia</a> na <a href="Gris">Gris</a>.

title: Sidarta
text:
Sidarta (Siddharta Gautama, o Buddha Gautama) i man bilong <a href="India">India</a>. Em i stap long India 2500 yia bipo. Planti man o meri ol i kolim "<a href="Buda">Buda</a>" tasol.
Dispela man i bin stat <a href="budisim">budisim</a>, o lotu bilong ol Buda. 
Mama bilong Sidarta i karim long India long yia samting olsem 563 bipo Kraist. Em i dai pinis taim i gat 80 krismas. 
Igat planti olpela stori long Sidarta, o Buda. Ating sampela stori i tru na sampela stori i no tru. Tasol, manmeri bilong toksave histori, o toksave long taim bipo tru, ol i tingting i tru olsem Sidarta i stap long India 2500 yia bipo. 
Olpela stori ol i tok olsem papa bilong sidarta em i king. Taim i pikinini yet, Sidarta i got planti moni. Papa bilongen i holimpasim na Sidarta i no bungim wanpela trabel yet. Tasol taim Sidarta i kamap 29 krismas em i wok autsait long haus bilong king na i lukim 4pela samting: em i lukim olpela man, sikpela man, man i dai pinis, na gutpela man i gat no haus. Long dispela taim igo, Sidarta i tingting long dispela foapela samting tasol. I no ken hamamas yet. 
Olrait em i lusim haus long king na em i go long bus. Em i bungim narapela man ol i traim painim hamamas long pasin asetik. Dispela i min ol i laik kaikai liklik tru, na ol i no laik moni na haus bilongen. Sidarta tu, em i traim painim hamamas long pasin asetik long taim bilong 7pela yia. Olrait em i save dispela pasin i nogut. 
Olrait em i tingting long laip bilongen longpela taim tru. Em i wokim wokim <a href="meditesen">meditesen</a>. Meditesen em i pasin i sindaun long graun na i no tok, na i painim hamamas insait long en. Olrait wanpela de em i sidaun long diwai na em i painim pinis <a href="enlaitmen">enlaitmen</a>. Enlaitmen i min dispela man o meri i no gat wanpela trabel yet insait long het bilongen. I gat hamamas tru tumas. Nau ol i kolim dispela diwai diwai bilong enlaitmen. 
Long dispela taim Sidarta i painim pinis ol save ol i kolim <a href="foapela%20tok%20tru">foapela tok tru</a>. Ol i as bilong <a href="budisim">budisim</a>, o lotu bilong ol Buda.

title: Ferdinand de Saussure
text:
Ferdinand de Saussure (<a href="Novemba%2026">Novemba 26</a>, <a href="1857">1857</a> - <a href="Februeri%2022">Februeri 22</a>, <a href="1913">1913</a>) em i man bilong <a href="Swisalan">Swisalan</a>.
Saussure i bikpela long histori long <a href="lingwistikis">lingwistikis</a> long <a href="20th%20senseri">20th senseri</a>. Em i tingting pinis lingwistikis i olsem kain long save bilong olgeta symbol, em i kolim semiolosi (nau <a href="semiotikis">semiotikis</a>.)
Buk bilong em i "Cours de linguistique générale" (Skulim long general lingwistikis).

title: Philippe Cuénoud
text:
Philippe Cuénoud (1968-) saientis bilong <a href="Swisalan">Swisalan</a>, toktok bilong em <a href="Tok%20Pranis">Tok Pranis</a>. Em i gat window bilong fes.
Em i wok sompela mun long Papua New Guinea long krismas 1993 na 1994 long Wau na <a href="Madang">Madang</a>. Em lainim Tok Pisin na painim tupela nupela kain binatang na wokim liklik wok wantaim <a href="Larry%20Orsak">Larry Orsak</a>. Em i speselist bilong binatang na sayor na pablisim long <a href="ivolusan">ivolusan</a> bilong ol . Em wok wanpela krismas long indastri bilong marasin, long kampani Covance, tasol ol i rausim em. Em wok sompela yia long skul tu, tasol ol rausim em tu.
Nau em wok long sevim wara na eneji.
Em painim nupela kain plaua long Swisalan .
linked_text: Philippe Cuénoud (1968-) saientis bilong Swisalan, toktok bilong em Tok Pranis. Em i gat window bilong fes. Em i wok sompela mun long Papua New Guinea long krismas 1993 na 1994 long Wau na Madang. Em lainim Tok Pisin na painim tupela nupela kain binatang na wokim liklik wok wantaim [[Larry Orsak]]. Em i speselist bilong binatang na sayor na pablisim long [[ivolusan]] bilong ol . Em wok wanpela krismas long indastri bilong marasin, long kampani Covance, tasol ol i rausim em. Em wok sompela yia long skul tu, tasol ol rausim em tu. Nau em wok long sevim wara na eneji. Em painim nupela kain plaua long Swisalan .

title: Planet
text:
Planet (long <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "Planet") istap nem bilong olgeta ston i go nabaut <a href="San">San</a> o narapela <a href="sta">sta</a>. Ol planet istap raun. <a href="Mun%20%28Giraun%29">Mun</a> istap nem bilong ol liklik ston i go nabaut planet. <a href="San">San</a> bilong yumi i gat etpela planet. <a href="Piluto">Piluto</a> bin planet tasol nau olgeta manmeri bilong <a href="Estronomi">Estronomi</a> i kolim dispela <a href="liklik%20planet">liklik planet</a>. Istap tupela narapela <a href="liklik%20planet">liklik planet</a>, <a href="Seres%20%28liklik%20planet%29">Seres</a> na <a href="Eris%20%28liklik%20planet%29">Eris</a>.
Nem "planet" i kam long Tok <a href="Girik%20%28language%29">Girik</a>: πλανήτης ("planetes"). I min "welman" o "samting i go". Manmeri bilong <a href="Estronomi">Estronomi</a> i got save long 209 narapela planet. Olgeta dispela i go nabaut narapela <a href="sta">sta</a>. 
Ol I Go Nabaut <a href="San">San</a>.
Nem bilong olgeta planet i go nabaut <a href="San">San</a> i kam long nem bilong god bilong <a href="Rom%20%28biktaun%29">Rom</a>. Nem bilong sampela <a href="Mun">Mun</a> i kam long stori <a href="Shakespeare">Shakespeare</a> raitim.
Planet.
Dispela istap <a href="ol%20planet">ol planet</a> i go nabaut <a href="San">San</a>. Numba wan istap klostu long <a href="San">San</a>.

title: Siamani
text:
Siaman(i) oa Je(r)man(i) (, ) emi wanpela <a href="kantri">kantri</a> long <a href="Yurop">Yurop</a>. 
Em i stap arere long kantri <a href="Pranis">Pranis</a> na <a href="Holan">Holan</a>. Kampani na gavman bilong Siamani i bin bosim noten hap bilong <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a> long taim bipo inap long yia 1914. Oli kolim dispela hap bilong Papua Niugini long dispela taim <a href="Siaman%20Niugini">Siaman Niugini</a>.
Siamani em i asples bilong <a href="Martin%20Luther">Martin Luther</a> na <a href="Albert%20Einstein">Albert Einstein</a>.
<a href="Kapitol">Kapitol</a> na bikpela taun bilong kantri emi <a href="Berlin">Berlin</a>.

title: Famili bilong tokples
text:
Wanpela famili bilong tokples emi wanpela grup bilong ol tokples. Olgeta tokples insait long wanpela famili igat wanpela tumbuna tokples tasol long taim bifo.
Igat planti famili bilong tokples long wol. Igat tok long wanem famili tru istap na wanem tokples istap insait long wanem famili.

Sampela tokples ol i nogat famili bilong ol, olsem <a href="Tok%20Bask">Tok Bask</a>, <a href="Tokples%20Siapan">Tokples Siapan</a>, na <a href="Tokples%20Korea">Tokples Korea</a>.

title: Binumarien
text:
Binumarien em i wanpela tok ples bilong <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Ol lain husat i save tokim Binumarien yet i save kolim dispela tok ples "Afaqinna ufa". Ol Binumarien lain i stap 1200 nabaut, na ol i stap long Kainantu Distrik long Eastern Highlands Province.
Long memori bilong ol lapun, bifo, ol Binumarien lain i bin planti. Tasol namba bilong en i bin i go daun as olsem planti i dai bilong fait na sik malaria. Long 1973, i bin i gat ol 117 Binumarien manmeri tasol, pikinini wantaim. Nau ol Binumarien i stap isi isi wantaim ol narapela hauslain na ol i stap long wanpela ples antap we ol i no save kisim sik bilong malaria tumas long en.

title: Wik
text:
Wik em i <a href="taim">taim</a> i gat seven <a href="de">de</a>. Wanpela <a href="yia">yia</a> i gat 52 wik na wanpela o tupela de.
Long <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>, nem bilong ol de bilong wik i kam long <a href="got">got</a> bilong pipel <a href="Nos">Nos</a>, tasol <a href="sarere">sarere</a> i kam long <a href="Saten">Saten</a>, i got bilong pipel <a href="Rom">Rom</a>. Long <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a>, sampela nem bilong de i wankain nem long Tok Inglis, tasol nem bilong Trinde na Fonde i kamap bilong <a href="namba">namba</a>.
Nem bilong sarere na sande wantaim i <a href="wiken">wiken</a>.
linked_text: Wik em i taim i gat seven [[de]]. Wanpela [[yia]] i gat 52 wik na wanpela o tupela de. Long Tok Inglis, nem bilong ol de bilong wik i kam long got bilong pipel Nos, tasol [[sarere]] i kam long Saten, i got bilong pipel [[Rom]]. Long [[Tok Pisin]], sampela nem bilong de i wankain nem long Tok Inglis, tasol nem bilong Trinde na Fonde i kamap bilong namba. Nem bilong sarere na sande wantaim i wiken.

title: Auckland Grammar School
text:
Auckland Grammar School emi wanpela sikul bilong ol yangpela man tasol long ples <a href="Auckland">Auckland</a> long <a href="Niu%20Zilan">Niu Zilan</a>.
Oli skulim ol yangpela man istat long Yia 9 inap long Yia 13. Na tu long dispela sikul istap sampela sumatin ikam long narapela hap husat isave silip long haus bilong sikul.
Dispela sikul emi bikpela olsem i winim klostu olgeta narapela sikul long Niu Zilan.

title: Gyeonggi
text:
Gyeonggi (<a href="Tok%20Korea">Tok Korea</a>: 경기도) em i wanpela provins long <a href="Saut%20Korea">Saut Korea</a>. Insait em i gat tupela bikpela taun <a href="Seoul">Seoul</a> na <a href="Incheon">Incheon</a>, tasol dispela tupela taun i indipenden long provins. Long Notes em i gat arere wantaim <a href="Not%20Korea">Not Korea</a>, Sautem wantaim <a href="Not%20Chungcheong">Not Chungcheong</a>, Ist wantaim <a href="Gangwon">Gangwon</a>.
<a href="Kapitol">Kapitol</a> long Gyeonggi i <a href="Suwon">Suwon</a>.
linked_text: Gyeonggi (Tok Korea: 경기도) em i wanpela provins long Saut Korea. Insait em i gat tupela bikpela taun Seoul na Incheon, tasol dispela tupela taun i indipenden long provins. Long Notes em i gat arere wantaim Not Korea, Sautem wantaim Not Chungcheong, Ist wantaim Gangwon. [[Kapitol]] long Gyeonggi i Suwon.

title: Ivolusan
text:
Ivolusan (Inglis: Evolution) emi senis i kamap long milian yia, na pradusim planti kain enimol na planis. Ol senis liklik tasol ol bikam bigpela bihain longpela taim.
<a href="Charles%20Darwin">Charles Darwin</a> em i fes saintis i tingim long ivolusen. Em tingting ivolusan wok bikos long <a href="netirel%20seleksan">netirel seleksan</a>. Em tingting olsem ol tumbuna bilong man wankain mangi (monkeys), na ol i senis long bigepla taim (olsem 3 milian krismas) na bikam ol man na meri. Ol arapela enimol na planis tu i kamap long ivolusan.
Bihain Darwin ol saientis stadi unives na painim nois bilong criesen bilong em. Ol i kolim criesen bilong unives <a href="bigpela%20bang">bigpela bang</a> (Inglis: Big Bang).
Ino olgeta manmeri bilip long ivolusan. Planti lain bilip olsem Papa God crietim wol na Adam na Eve. Ol i tingting ivolusan giaman.

Ol i tingting ivolusan giaman.

title: Benedict XVI
text:

title: Jisas
text:
Jisas i man i stap long kantri Juda (nau <a href="Israel">Israel</a>) 2000 yia bipo. Nau ol i kolim olsem Jisas Krais(t) o Krais(t) tu. 
Stori long Jisas i kam long <a href="baibel">baibel</a>. Taim bilong laip bilong Jisas, no man o meri i bin raitim stori long en. Man o meri i raitim baibel ol i no bung Jisas. Olrait sampela man o meri ol i tok stori bilong baibel ol i tru, na sampela ol i tok ol i no tru. Sampela i tok sampela pat i tru na sampela pat i no tru. 
Laip bilong Jisas.
Papamama bilong Jisas ol i bilong <a href="Judaisim">lotu bilong Juda</a>, na Jisas i bilong lotu bilong Juda tu. Long dispela taim, man bilong <a href="Roma">Roma</a> i bosim kantri bilong Juda. 
Taim Jisas i gat 30 o 35 krismas em i save wokabaut long kantri bilong Juda na i save skulim pipel long lotuim <a href="Got">Got</a> na laikim narapela manmeri. Em i toktok olsem Got em i laikim manmeri, na manmeri i mas laikim Got na i mas laikim wanpela narapela. 
Long baibel ol i tok olsem Jisas i save wokim gutpela masik olsem kamapim planti pis long baskit, tanim wara igo long wain, rausim sik long manmeri i gat sik lepa, mekim manmeri i dai pinis na ol i gat laip gen. 
Olrait Jisas i kamap femas na em i go long <a href="Yerusalem">Yerusalem</a>. Tasol ol bos bilong Juda na ol gavman bilong Roma ol i fret Jisas i kamap bikpela bos bilong olgeta man o meri bilong dispela kantri. Olrait ol i nelim Jisas long kros na ol i letim hia inap taim long i dai pinis. Long dispela taim, dispela we long kilim man i dai pinis, gavman bilong Roma ol i yusim tumas. 
Taim Jisas i dai pinis pren bilongen ol i planim long hul insait long ston. Tasol sampela de bihain bodi bilong Jisas i no stap long hul yet. Sampela i tingting Jisas i got laip gen na i save go long heven.
Lotu.
Man o meri husat i tingting Jisas i got laip gen ol i kolim <a href="Kristen">Kristen</a>. Kristen i tingting em i tru, olsem Jisas em Got i kam long graun. 
Planti man o meri i no <a href="Kristen">Kristen</a>, tasol ol i tingting Jisas i bin toktok planti gutpela samting, na Jisas i bin skulim planti gutpela pasin.

title: Plak bilong Papua Niugini
text:
Plak bilong <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a> i mak olsem ofisel plak bilong kantri long <a href="Julai%201">Julai 1</a>, <a href="1971">1971</a>. Plak i soim <a href="Sauten%20Kros">Sauten Kros</a> na <a href="kumul">kumul</a>. Wanpela meri sumatin igat 15 krismas, <a href="Susan%20Huhume">Susan Huhume</a>, i wokim dispela plak na winim nesenel resis long 1971 long wokim nupela plak bilong kantri.
Ol retpela na blakpela kala i stap olsem kala bilong kastom bilong taim bifo long sampela ol lain long Papua Niugini. Plak bilong <a href="Siaman%20Niugini">Siaman Niugini</a> i blakpela, waitpela na retpela pinis. Kumul i sanap tu long <a href="nesenel%20mak%20bilong%20Papua%20Niugini">nesenel mak bilong kantri</a> ().
Olpela plak bilong Papua Niugini bipo.
<br clear=all>

title: Sel
text: Wanpela sel emi liklik moa yet samting i stap laif. Olgeta samting i gat laif olsem diwai, ol enimol, na ol manmeri i gat planti tumas sel. Dispela graun i gat planti difren kain sel, sampela ol save kisim lait b'long san na wokim kaikai b'long ol yet. Narapla kain sel, olsem dispela kain ol manmeri i gat save kaikai narapla samting. Yu no inap lukim sel, ol liklik tumas. Wanpela sel i gat difren kain samting b'long helpim em wok. Yu bai kolim dispela samting organel. Wanpela organel emi save givim tok long olgeta sel long wokim difren kain samting, olsem protin, na ol narapela sel. Nem b'long dispela organel emi Nuklios.

title: Kemistri
text:
Kemistri (Inglis: chemistry) emi saiens i stadi mata (matter). Saientis i wokim kemistri ol i kolim kemist (chemist).
Long mata i gat liklik hap ol i kolim <a href="molekel">molekel</a> (molecule), na liklik moa hap ol i kolim atom. Ol kemis kolim kain bilong atom elemen na putim ol elemen long wanpela tebel: periodic table of elements. I gat 100 elemen long wol.

title: Krowesia
text:
Krowesia (<a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "Croatia", <a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>: "Hrvatska") em i wanpela <a href="kantri">kantri</a> long <a href="Yurop">Yurop</a>. <a href="Kapitol">Kapitol</a> na nambawan bigpela taun tumas bilong dispela kantri em i <a href="Zagreb">Zagreb</a>. <a href="Tokples">Tokples</a> bilong Krowesia em i <a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>. Krowesia i gat 20 <a href="kaunti">kaunti</a>, olsem provins, na <a href="biktaun">biktaun</a> Zagreb, na bikpela bilong en em i 56.594 km2. Em i gat <a href="klaimet">klaimet</a> bilong <a href="Solwara%20bilong%20Graun%20long%20namel">Solwara bilong Graun long namel</a> (<a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "Mediterranean Sea") na <a href="kontinen">kontinen</a>. <a href="Solwara">Solwara</a> bilong Krowesia em i gat mo long 1000 <a href="ailan">ailan</a>. Krowesia i gat 4,290,612 <a href="manmeri">manmeri</a> na <a href="lotu">lotu</a> bilong planti manmeri em i <a href="lotu%20Kristen">lotu Kristen</a> (<a href="Katolik">Katolik</a>).
Long taim bifo Krowesia em i hap bilong <a href="Yugoslavia">Yugoslavia</a>. Long yia <a href="1991">1991</a> taim Krowesia i bin kamap olsem wanpela <a href="independen">independen</a> kantri. Bihain long <a href="1995">1995</a> i no bin gat <a href="pait">pait</a> namel long Krowesia na <a href="Sebia">Sebia</a>.
Krowesia em i wanwan memba kantri bilong <a href="Yunaitid%20Neishins">Yunaitid Neishins</a>, <a href="NATO">NATO</a>, <a href="WTO">WTO</a>, <a href="CEFTA">CEFTA</a> na <a href="Kaunsil%20bilong%20Yurop">Kaunsil bilong Yurop</a>. Bihain long yia <a href="2013">2013</a> Krowesia em bai memba bilong <a href="Yunion%20bilong%20Yurop">Yunion bilong Yurop</a>.
linked_text: Krowesia (Tok Inglis: "Croatia", [[Tok Krowesia]]: "Hrvatska") em i wanpela [[kantri]] long [[Yurop]]. [[Kapitol]] na nambawan bigpela taun tumas bilong dispela kantri em i Zagreb. [[Tokples]] bilong Krowesia em i [[Tok Krowesia]]. Krowesia i gat 20 [[kaunti]], olsem provins, na biktaun Zagreb, na bikpela bilong en em i 56.594 km2. Em i gat klaimet bilong Solwara bilong Graun long namel (Tok Inglis: "Mediterranean Sea") na [[kontinen]]. Solwara bilong Krowesia em i gat mo long 1000 [[ailan]]. Krowesia i gat 4,290,612 manmeri na [[lotu]] bilong planti manmeri em i [[lotu Kristen]] ([[Katolik]]). Long taim bifo Krowesia em i hap bilong Yugoslavia. Long yia [[1991]] taim Krowesia i bin kamap olsem wanpela independen kantri. Bihain long [[1995]] i no bin gat pait namel long Krowesia na [[Sebia]]. Krowesia em i wanwan memba kantri bilong Yunaitid Neishins, NATO, WTO, CEFTA na Kaunsil bilong Yurop. Bihain long yia 2013 Krowesia em bai memba bilong Yunion bilong Yurop.

title: Intanet
text:
Intanet ("Internet" long Tok Inglis) em i planti rot ol i bungim planti <a href="komputa">komputa</a> long olgeta graun, olsem haus bilon <a href="spaida">spaida</a>. Dispela rot ol i mekim long rop ol i save karim meses, o liklik pas. Dispela pas ol i raitim long tok ol i kolim <a href="Intanet%20Protokol">Intanet Protokol</a> (IP).
Tede planti pipel ol i yusim intanet bilong kain kain samting: 
Taim bipo.
Intanet em i kirap long <a href="Amerika">Amerika</a> long yia 1969 long <a href="ARPA">ARPA</a>. Em nau, World Wide Web (o "haus bilong spaida em i bikpela olsem olgeta wol") ol i kirapim long <a href="CERN">CERN</a> long <a href="Swis">Swis</a> long samting olsem 1990. Olrait taim bihain dispela taim planti man o meri i bungim planti kompyuta igo long intanet. 
Tede i gat samting olsem 9.000.000.000 (nainpela bilion) pes long intanet. Na tu, i gat samting olsem 200.000.000 (tu handred milion) adres bilong imel long wol.
linked_text: Intanet ("Internet" long Tok Inglis) em i planti rot ol i bungim planti komputa long olgeta graun, olsem haus bilon spaida. Dispela rot ol i mekim long rop ol i save karim meses, o liklik pas. Dispela pas ol i raitim long tok ol i kolim Intanet Protokol (IP). Tede planti pipel ol i yusim intanet bilong kain kain samting:  Taim bipo. Intanet em i kirap long [[Amerika]] long yia 1969 long ARPA. Em nau, World Wide Web (o "haus bilong spaida em i bikpela olsem olgeta wol") ol i kirapim long CERN long Swis long samting olsem 1990. Olrait taim bihain dispela taim planti man o meri i bungim planti kompyuta igo long intanet.  Tede i gat samting olsem 9.000.000.000 (nainpela bilion) pes long intanet. Na tu, i gat samting olsem 200.000.000 (tu handred milion) adres bilong imel long [[wol]].

title: Ronald Reagan
text: Ronald Wilson Reagan (Februeri 6, 1911 - Jun 5, 2004) i presiden namba 40 bilong Amerika. Em i kamap presiden tupela taim: long yia 1981 na long yia 1985. Ronald Reagan em i pikinini bilong Jack Reagan na Nelle Wilson Reagan. Bipo long taim Reagan i kamap presiden, em i kamap man i pilai long drama long redio, piksa o muvi na televisen.

title: Saipras

title: Ti
text:
Ti i samting ol i drink. Ol i kisim ti long "Camellia sinensis" planim.
Wok bilong ol kantri.
Long 2003, ol kantri bilong wol i bin mekim millon ton long olgeta yia. Long 2008, ol kantri bilong wol i bin mekim moa long million ton bilong ti. <a href="Saina">Saina</a>, <a href="India">India</a>, <a href="Kenya">Kenya</a>, <a href="Sri%20Lanka">Sri Lanka</a>, na <a href="Teki">Teki</a> i mekim bikpela tumas ti long wol.
Dispela lista soim hamas ti (long ton) ol kantri i mekim. Save i kamap bilong "Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO) of the United Nations" long Janueri 2010.

title: Kuk
text:
Kuk i <a href="at">at</a> na <a href="saiens">saiens</a> long kukim kaikai long hat. I gat planti pasin bilong kuk long wol. Pasin bilong kuk na kuk bilong arakain kantri ol i soim kalsa na pasin bilong nau.
Olgeta ol i kuk. Manmeri i kuk long haus bilong en, na man kuk i kuk tu long <a href="haus%20kaikai">haus kaikai</a>.
Redim kuk long hat o paia i samting bilong man tasol. Ating em i stat 2 milien yia bipo, tasol i no gat samting i sapotim dispela tingting. I gat mak bipo bilong 1 milien yia tasol.
Kamap bikpela bilong <a href="egrikalsa">egrikalsa</a>, <a href="bisnis">bisnis</a>, <a href="tret">tret</a>, na pasin long kamap long arakain manmeri ol i givim man kuk planti nupela kaikai. Nupela samting na teknoloji ol i kamap bikpela planti pasin bilong kuk. Sampela man kuk nau ol i yusim saiens long givim tes bilong kaikai moa tes.

text: Cuyonon em i tokples blong sampla Visayas ailan na em i toktok i stap long nambis blong <a href="Palawan">Palawan</a> ailan na Cuyo ailan long Palawan provins long <a href="Filipin">Filipin</a>. title: Abus
text:
Abus o animal () em i wanpela kain tingting i gat laip. Ol yet i no inap mekim <a href="kaikai">kaikai</a>. Em i save kaikai sayor o arapela abus.
Sampela i gat bun, ol i kolim Vertebrates. Egsempel: <a href="Pisin">Pisin</a>, <a href="Mamel">Mamel</a>, <a href="Reptail">Reptail</a> na <a href="Pis">Pis</a>.
Arapela no gat bun, ol i kolim Invertebrates. Egsempel: <a href="Binatang">Binatang</a>.
Egsempel:
<a href="Pisin">Pisin</a> (Aves) save palai na wokim kiau: balus, kakaruk, kumul, muruk, etc.
<a href="Mamel">Mamel</a> (Mammalia) igat gras na ol i no wokim kiau (iksept nil kapul): sikau, kapul, bulmakau, man, <a href="bea">bea</a> (bear), etc.
<a href="Reptail">Reptail</a> (Reptilia) i no nap palai na i no gat grass na ol i wokim kiau: pukpuk, snek, etc.
<a href="Pis">Pis</a> (Pisces) stap long wara.
<a href="Binatang">Binatang</a> (Arthropoda) liklik tumas: bataplai, anis, etc.
linked_text: Abus o animal () em i wanpela kain tingting i gat laip. Ol yet i no inap mekim kaikai. Em i save kaikai sayor o arapela abus. Sampela i gat bun, ol i kolim Vertebrates. Egsempel: [[Pisin]], [[Mamel]], [[Reptail]] na [[Pis]]. Arapela no gat bun, ol i kolim Invertebrates. Egsempel: [[Binatang]]. Egsempel: [[Pisin]] (Aves) save palai na wokim kiau: balus, kakaruk, kumul, muruk, etc. [[Mamel]] (Mammalia) igat gras na ol i no wokim kiau (iksept nil kapul): sikau, kapul, bulmakau, man, [[bea]] (bear), etc. [[Reptail]] (Reptilia) i no nap palai na i no gat grass na ol i wokim kiau: pukpuk, snek, etc. [[Pis]] (Pisces) stap long wara. [[Binatang]] (Arthropoda) liklik tumas: bataplai, anis, etc.

title: Palawan
text:
Palawan (ofisel nem: Palawan Provins, <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "Province of Palawan", Tok Filipin: "Probinsya ng Palawan", Tok "Cuyonon": "Probinsya i'ang Palawan"; "Paragua") i ailans provins blong <a href="Filipin">Filipin</a>.
Palawan i stap long MIMAROPA rijin o Namba 4-B rijin. Palawan i bikpla olsem long ol provins blong Filipin. Kapitol blong en i <a href="Puerto%20Princesa%20City">Puerto Princesa City</a>.
Narapla nem: "”The Philippines' Last Frontier.”"
Olgeta hap graun.
Ailans blong Palawan i stap long namel long Mindoro ailans long not-is na <a href="Borneo">Borneo</a> ailan long saut-wes. Palawan ailans i stap tu long namel long Wes Filipin Si long wes na Sulu Si long is.
Nem blong Palawan i kam long nem blong bikpla ailan blong ol ailans blong Palawan, nem blong en i Palawan tu. Palawan i mekim blong planti ailan, Palawan (Bikpla ailan) na planti liklik ailan raun en, wan kain, Busuanga ailan, Coron ailan, na Culion ailan (We ol manmeri husat i gat sik leprosy i stap long taim bipo.) long not. Balabac ailan long saut.
Long is, i gat Cuyo ailans, Magsaysay ailans, na Cagayancillio ailans (We Tubattaha Reef i stap longen). Long wes, Palawan i gat planti liklik ailans blong Kalayaan. Palawan i gat planti hap. Em i 23 municipalities.
Histori.
Bipotaim histori blong Palawan i bin painimaut long <a href="Robert%20Fox">Robert Fox</a>. Long yia 1970's em i painim wanpla bun blong <a href="Homo%20Sapiens">Homo Sapiens</a>, husat i gat 50,000 yia tasol. Bun ya i gat moa krismas olsem long ol bun blong Filipin. Robert Fox givim nem blong bun "Tabon Man" as bun i bin painim long Tabon Cave long Quezon Municipality, i stap saut long Palawan (Bikpla ailan).
Palawán na <a href="Tagbanwa">Tagbanwa</a> manmeri em i nambawan manmeri i stap long Palawan. Long taim bipo yet, em i tret long narapla manmeri blong narapla ailan husat i gat bot. Palawan (Bikpla ailan) tu i gat Batak manmeri. (Em i nogat Batek blong <a href="Malaysia">Malaysia</a> o Batak blong <a href="Sumatra">Sumatra</a>.) Em i wanblut long ol Aeta manmeri husat i stap long narapla ailan blong Filipin. Olsem na Batak manmeri tu i wanblut long ol <a href="Melanesian">Melanesian</a> manmeri.
Manmeri i stap long narapla ailan blong Palawan, em i Cuyonon manmeri long ol Cuyo ailan, Calamianes manmeri long Calamian ailan.
Long 20th century Palawan i kisim planti imigren husat i stap long narapla ailan laik Luzon mainland, Ilo-Ilo provins na narapla ailan. Planti em i stap long Narra municipality na Puerto Princesa City.

title: Tok Aialan
text:
Tok Aialan i tokples bilong kantri <a href="Ripablik%20bilong%20Aialan">Ripablik bilong Aialan</a>. Tok Aialan em i ofisel tokples bilong dispela kantri, tasol planti manmeri long Aialan save toktok long <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a> na i nogat planti i yusim Tok Aialan nau. Tok Aialan bai mak olsem wanpela ofisel tokples bilong long yia 2007.
Tok Aialan em i wanpela tokples ikam long <a href="famili%20long%20tokples%20long%20Indo-Yurop">famili long tokples long Indo-Yurop</a>, na bilong lain <a href="tokples%20long%20Kelt">tokples long Kelt</a> bilong dispela famili.

title: Ripablik bilong Saina
text:
Republik bilong Saina () emi wanpela kantri long <a href="Esia">Esia</a> istap long <a href="Taiwan">Taiwan</a> ailan. 
Taim bipo <a href="kapitol">kapitol</a> bilong em i bin <a href="Nanjing">Nanjing</a> tasol nau dispela taun istap insait long <a href="Ol%20Manmeri%20Ripablik%20bilong%20Saina">Ol Manmeri Ripablik bilong Saina</a>. text:

Buk bilong Momon emi bikpela buk long sekred ritim bilong "Momons" o "(Tok Inglis:) The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints". Olpela manmeri seim buk pastaim long yia 1830, mekim public long Joseph Smith, Jr. na taital; ("Tok Inglis") "The Book of Mormon: An Account Written by the Hand of Mormon upon Plates Taken from the Plates of Nephi." Dispela buk sapos tubi olsem laik <a href="Baibel">Baibel</a>.

title: Kristen
text:
Ol Kristen ol i man o meri ol i lotuim <a href="Jisas">Jisas</a>, o Krais(t), na ol i tingting Jisas em i <a href="Got">Got</a> i kam long Graun. 
I gat samting olsem 2000 milion man o meri ol i kolim yet Kristen long Graun. 
Insait long Kristen, i gat kainkain lain, olsem:
Long Kristen sosaiti mipela I bilip olsem jisas em I ridima na em salvation bilong mipela ol man,meri.
Mipela I bilip more olsem god papa I laikim tumas mipela ol man meri long dispela graun na em I giving pikinini bilong em olsem sakrifais long sin bilong mipela,olsem tasol usait man o meri I bilip long dispela Bai ino lus,tasol gat laip (Jn 3:16)

title: Kadinol daireksion
text:
Kadinol direksion o kadinol point bin ol fo big direksion o point bilong kampas: <a href="not">not</a>, <a href="ist">ist</a>, <a href="saut">saut</a> na <a href="west">west</a>. Dis direksion bin tu raitim long smol we as N, I, S and W long <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a>.
North and south are directed towards the north and south <a href="pole">pole</a>s of the <a href="Earth">Earth</a>. The Earth's rotation defines east and west. The sun rises in the morning on east, and sets in the evening on west.
If a needle is <a href="magnetism">magnetised</a> and allowed to move freely (for example floated on water) it will align itself with the Earth's <a href="magnetic%20field">magnetic field</a> which is almost in the same direction with north. The direction of the needle in this situation is called <a href="North%20Magnetic%20Pole">magnetic north</a> which differs from <a href="geographical%20north">geographical north</a> by few <a href="degree">degree</a>s.
Cardinal directions in world cultures.

title: COVID-19 pandemic
text: COVID-19 pandemic, a.k.a. coronavirus pandemic, em i stap nupela pandemic bilong coronavirus disease 2019. COVID-19 em i mekim bilong <a href="SARS-CoV-2">SARS-CoV-2</a>. Tude em i gat moa long 21,950,000 ol keis, na moa long 770,000 manmeri i dai pinis long COVID-19. Namba wan keis em i insait long Wuhan, <a href="Ol%20Manmeri%20Ripablik%20bilong%20Saina">Saina</a>, na stap nau insait long 188 kantri na teritori. <a href="Ol%20Yunaitet%20Stet">Ol Yunaitet Stet</a> em i namba wan kantri wantaim moa tru keis insait long graun (moa long 5,400,000).
linked_text: COVID-19 pandemic, a.k.a. coronavirus pandemic, em i stap nupela pandemic bilong coronavirus disease 2019. COVID-19 em i mekim bilong [[SARS-CoV-2]]. title: Papua Niugini
text:
Papua Niugini em i wanpela kantri long rijen <a href="Melanesia">Melanesia</a> long <a href="Pasifik">Pasifik</a>. Giraun bilong kantri i stap long isten hap bilong <a href="Niugini%20Ailan">Niugini Ailan</a> na tu long ol narapela ailan olsem <a href="Niu%20Briten">Niu Briten</a>, <a href="Niu%20Ailan">Niu Ailan</a>, <a href="Bogenvil">Bogenvil</a>, <a href="Manus">Manus</a>, na planti moa.
Stori bilong kantri.
Sampela manmeri ikam long Niugini Ailan long nambawan taim long faivpela ten tausen (50,000) yia i go pinis. Ol pipol bilong <a href="Hailans%20Rijen">Hailans</a> i wokim gaden long nain tausen (9,000) yia i go pinis - em i klostu nambawan taim long wol long wokim gaden.
Olsem fopela tausen (4,000) yia i go pinis, ol lain oli kolim <a href="Ostronisien">Ostronisien</a> i kamap long Papua Niugini, na oli bringim ol pik, pasin bilong hukim pis, pasin bilong wokim pot, na ol nupela tokples i kam.
Olsem tri handet (300) yia i go pinis, <a href="kaukau">kaukau</a> i kam long <a href="Saut%20Amerika">Saut Amerika</a>. Kaukau i winim <a href="taro">taro</a> long karim planti kaikai, na nau namba bilong ol manmeri i go antap long <a href="Hailans%20Rijen">Hailans</a> na sampela ol narapela hap.
Dispela nem "Papua Niugini" i kamap long tok "Papua", hap tok bilong <a href="Malesia">Malesia</a> long kain gras bilong ol manmeri bilong Melanesia, na tok "Niu Gini", i kam long wanpela man bilong <a href="Spen">Spen</a>, <a href="Y%C3%B1igo%20Ortiz%20de%20Retez">Yñigo Ortiz de Retez</a>, husait i tingim lukluk bilong ol manmeri bilong Niugini i wankain ol manmeri bilong hap <a href="Gini">Gini</a> long <a href="Afrika">Afrika</a>.
Long yia 1883, kantri <a href="Briten">Briten</a> i kam long <a href="Sauten%20Rijen">Sauten Rijen</a> na tokaut olsem em i giraun bilong ol nau. Ol i kirapim gavman bilong dispela hap na givim nem "British New Guinea", o "Niugini bilong Briten". Kapitol bilong dispela gavman em i Pot Mosbi.
Long yia 1884, kantri <a href="Jemani">Jemani</a> i kam long <a href="Ailans%20Rijen">Ailans Rijen</a> na <a href="Momase%20Rijen">Momase Rijen</a> na tokaut olsem em i giraun bilong ol nau. Ol i no kirapim gavman tru pastaim, tasol oli tokim Kampani bilong Niugini (Tok Siaman: "Neuguinea-Kompanie") long bosim dispela giraun. Nambawan taun bilong dispela kampani oli kolim "Herbertshöhe" long Tok Siaman. Nau yumi save long dispela taun long nem <a href="Kokopo">Kokopo</a>. Long yia 1899, gavman bilong Jemani i tokim kampani olsem i mas pinis long bosim giraun, na gavman i kirapim ofis bilong gavman long bosim Niugini bilong Jemani.
Taim wo i stat long 1915, ami bilong <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> i rausim gavman bilong Jemani na bosim tupela giraun: "Papua" (<a href="Sauten%20Rijen">Sauten Rijen</a>) na "New Guinea" (<a href="Ailans%20Rijen">Ailans Rijen</a> na <a href="Momase%20Rijen">Momase Rijen</a>). Wo i pinis long 1918, na bihain Ostrelia i kisim tokorait long <a href="Lig%20bilong%20ol%20Kantri">Lig bilong ol Kantri</a> (Tok Inglis: "League of Nations") long bosim tupela giraun.
Wo i kamap gen long 1941, taim ami bilong <a href="Siapan">Siapan</a> i kam na holim planti hap long Niugini olsem <a href="Niu%20Ailan">Niu Ailan</a>, <a href="Manus">Manus</a>, <a href="Niu%20Briten">Niu Briten</a>, <a href="Bogenvil">Bogenvil</a>, <a href="Momase%20Rijen">Momase Rijen</a> na tu <a href="Oro">Oro</a> na <a href="Milen%20Be">Milen Be</a>. Planti pait i kamap long kainkain hap long kantri long dispela taim. Dispela wo i pinis long 1945.
Bihain long wo, Papua na Niugini i pas wantaim olsem wanpela giraun, wantaim nem Papua na Niugini, na Ostrelia i lukautim. Haus bilong Asembli, olsem Palamen, i stat long 1964. Long 1972 nupela ileksen i kamap long Palamen tru, na ol memba i makim <a href="Michael%20Somare">Michael Somare</a> olsem nambawan Praim Minista bilong kantri. Long dispela taim, nem bilong kantri i senis i go long Papua Niugini.
Long yia 1975, long 16 Septemba, Papua Niugini i kisim independens long Ostrelia, na em i sanap olsem wanpela kantri em yet nau. Michael Somare bilong <a href="Pangu%20Pati">Pangu Pati</a> i stap olsem Praim Minista inap long yia 1980, na long dispela taim Palamen i vot long rausim em na <a href="Julius%20Chan">Julius Chan</a> i kisim nambawan sia nau.
Long yia 1982, Michael Somare i winim vot na sanap olsem Praim Minista gen, tasol Palamen i rausim em long 1985 na givim dispela posisen i go long <a href="Paias%20Wingti">Paias Wingti</a>. Wingti i stap yet olsem Praim Minista bihain long ol ileksen bilong yia 1987, tasol Palamen i rausim em long 1988 na makim <a href="Rabbie%20Namaliu">Rabbie Namaliu</a>.
Traipela pait long Bogenvil i stat long yia 1988 i go long yia 1997. Klostu tupela ten tausen (20,000) manmeri i dai pinis long dispela pait.
Long yia 1992, <a href="Sir%20Julius%20Chan">Sir Julius Chan</a> i kisim pawa gen, inap long 1997, taim em i risain bihain long traubel wantaim <a href="Sandlain">Sandlain</a> long <a href="Bogenvil">Bogenvil</a>. Palamen i makim Bill Skate olsem Praim Minista long dispela taim. Long 1999, oli rausim em gen, na <a href="Sir%20Mekere%20Morauta">Sir Mekere Morauta</a> em i sanap olsem nupela Praim Minista bilong kantri.
Long ileksen bilong yia 2002, nupela pati bilong <a href="Sir%20Michael%20Somare">Sir Michael Somare</a>, <a href="Nesenel%20Alains">Nesenel Alains</a>, i wokim nupela gavman, na long nambawan taim long kantri, dispela gavman istap long faivpela yia inap long ol ileksen long yia 2007.
Long <a href="Ileksen%20bilong%20PNG%20palamen%2C%202007">nesenel ileksen bilong yia 2007</a>, <a href="Nesenel%20Alains">Nesenel Alains</a> i winim ol narapela pati na kirapim nupela gavman gen.
Giraun.
Hekte bilong kantri em i 452,860 km². Long planti hap long kantri igat ol maunten na bikbus istap. <a href="Maun%20Wilhelm">Maun Wilhelm</a> i winim ol narapela maunten long kantri: antap bilong em em i 4,509 m.
Arere long tupela traipela wara, <a href="wara%20Sepik">wara Sepik</a> na <a href="wara%20Flai">wara Flai</a>, igat ol bigpela hap olsem ples tais.
Papua Niugini i silip antap long <a href="Raun%20bilong%20Paia%20bilong%20Pasifik">Raun bilong Paia bilong Pasifik</a>, na olsem igat planti <a href="maunten%20i%20save%20pairap">maunten i save pairap</a>, na tu em i peles bilong <a href="ol%20guria">ol guria</a>. Long yia 1994 wanpela pairap bilong <a href="Tavurvur">Tavurvur</a> na <a href="Vulcan">Vulcan</a> i bagarapim <a href="Rabaul%20taun">Rabaul taun</a> olgeta.
Ol abus na diwai.
Bigpela hap bilong ol pisin na abus bilong Niugini Ailan i wanlain long sampela pisin na abus bilong Ostrelia. Ol lain bilong kapul, kaskas na ol narapela abus olsem we ol i save karim pikinini long paus, ol i no save silip long narapela kantri: oli stap long Niugini na Ostrelia tasol.
Long ol ailan bilong Papua Niugini, ol abus i narapela kain gen: i no gat ol kapul, kaskas na narapela abus olsem.
Antap long 700 kain (Tok Inglis: "species") bilong pisin istap long Papua Niugini.
Wanpela lain bilong ol pisin igat bigpela nem: ol <a href="kumul">kumul</a> (Tok Inglis: "bird of paradise"). Long <a href="Hailans%20Rijen">Hailans Rijen</a>, planti lain bilong ol pipol save kisim ol kumul long wokim bilas. Long wan handet inap long tri handet yia igo pinis, planti bigmeri long Yurop i laikim tru gras bilong kumul, na baim ol Yurop man long kam sutim ol pisin na salim. Nau kumul em i <a href="nesenel%20mak%20bilong%20Papua%20Niugini">nesenel mak bilong Papua Niugini</a>, na yumi lukim em long <a href="Plak%20bilong%20Papua%20Niugini">plak</a> bilong kantri.
Ol manmeri.
Igat antap long 5 milien manmeri oli silip long Papua Niugini. Klostu long hap milien i silip long ol bikpela taun olsem <a href="Pot%20Mosbi">Pot Mosbi</a>, <a href="Lae">Lae</a>, <a href="Maun%20Hagen">Maun Hagen</a>, <a href="Madang">Madang</a>, <a href="Wewak">Wewak</a>, <a href="Goroka">Goroka</a>, na <a href="Kokopo">Kokopo</a>. Bigpela hap tru bilong namba bilong ol manmeri bilong kantri i silip long ol peles.
Papua Niugini igat planti manmeri husait i kisim <a href="sik%20AIDS">sik AIDS</a>, na namba bilong ol i winim ol narapela kantri long Pasifik. Dispela namba i kamap bikpela kwiktaim nau.
Ol tokples.
Papua Niugini igat antap long 800 tokples. Dispela namba em i makim olsem wanpela ten tu pesen (12%) bilong olgeta tokples long <a href="Graun">wol</a>, na i no gat narapela kantri long wol i winim dispela namba bilong ol tokples. Igat tupela bigpela lain bilong ol tokples: ol <a href="tokples%20Papua">tokples Papua</a>, na ol <a href="tokples%20Ostronisia">tokples Ostronisia</a>.
Igat tripela tokples bilong <a href="Palamen">Palamen</a>: <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>, <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a> na <a href="Hiri%20Motu">Hiri Motu</a>, tasol tokples bilong gavman na bigpela hap bilong ol sikul em i Tok Inglis. Sampela sikul i yusim ol lokol tokples wantaim ol yangpela sumatin long halivim ol long lainim pasin bilong ridim na raitim. Tok Pisin em i nambawan tokples bilong kantri bilong wanem namba bilong ol manmeri i yusim, long ol taun na ol peles, i winim olgeta narapela tokples. Planti lain long <a href="Sentral%20Provins">Sentral Provins</a> na <a href="Gulf%20Provins">Gulf Provins</a> i save yusim Hiri Motu, na ol i no save yusim Tok Pisin tumas.
Planti manmeri i save long tupela o tripela o moa tokples. Planti ol tokples long kantri igat ananit long faiv tausen (5,000) manmeri tasol i save yusim.
Ol kastom.
Papua Niugini igat antap long wan tausen pasin bilong kastom, wantaim kainkain pasin bilong danis, singsing, katim diwai, wokim bilas, na ol narapela pasin bilong kastom.
Long sampela hap bilong kantri, ol sios i rausim bikpela hap bilong ol kastom pinis, tasol long ol narapela hap, kastom i stap yet na ol manmeri i bihainim kastom wantaim ol pasin bilong sios.
linked_text: Papua Niugini em i wanpela kantri long rijen [[Melanesia]] long Pasifik. Giraun bilong kantri i stap long isten hap bilong Niugini Ailan na tu long ol narapela ailan olsem [[Niu Briten]], [[Niu Ailan]], [[Bogenvil]], [[Manus]], na planti moa. Stori bilong kantri. Sampela manmeri ikam long Niugini Ailan long nambawan taim long faivpela ten tausen (50,000) yia i go pinis. Ol pipol bilong Hailans i wokim gaden long nain tausen (9,000) yia i go pinis - em i klostu nambawan taim long wol long wokim gaden. Olsem fopela tausen (4,000) yia i go pinis, ol lain oli kolim Ostronisien i kamap long Papua Niugini, na oli bringim ol pik, pasin bilong hukim pis, pasin bilong wokim pot, na ol nupela tokples i kam. Olsem tri handet (300) yia i go pinis, [[kaukau]] i kam long [[Saut Amerika]]. Kaukau i winim taro long karim planti kaikai, na nau namba bilong ol manmeri i go antap long Hailans na sampela ol narapela hap. Dispela nem "Papua Niugini" i kamap long tok "Papua", hap tok bilong [[Malesia]] long kain gras bilong ol manmeri bilong Melanesia, na tok "Niu Gini", i kam long wanpela man bilong [[Spen]], Yñigo Ortiz de Retez, husait i tingim lukluk bilong ol manmeri bilong Niugini i wankain ol manmeri bilong hap Gini long Afrika. Long yia 1883, kantri Briten i kam long Sauten Rijen na tokaut olsem em i giraun bilong ol nau. Ol i kirapim gavman bilong dispela hap na givim nem "British New Guinea", o "Niugini bilong Briten". Kapitol bilong dispela gavman em i Pot Mosbi. Long yia 1884, kantri Jemani i kam long Ailans Rijen na Momase Rijen na tokaut olsem em i giraun bilong ol nau. Ol i no kirapim gavman tru pastaim, tasol oli tokim Kampani bilong Niugini (Tok Siaman: "Neuguinea-Kompanie") long bosim dispela giraun. Nambawan taun bilong dispela kampani oli kolim "Herbertshöhe" long Tok Siaman. Nau yumi save long dispela taun long nem [[Kokopo]]. Long yia 1899, gavman bilong Jemani i tokim kampani olsem i mas pinis long bosim giraun, na gavman i kirapim ofis bilong gavman long bosim Niugini bilong Jemani. Taim wo i stat long 1915, ami bilong [[Ostrelia]] i rausim gavman bilong Jemani na bosim tupela giraun: "Papua" (Sauten Rijen) na "New Guinea" (Ailans Rijen na Momase Rijen). Wo i pinis long 1918, na bihain Ostrelia i kisim tokorait long Lig bilong ol Kantri (Tok Inglis: "League of Nations") long bosim tupela giraun. Wo i kamap gen long 1941, taim ami bilong [[Siapan]] i kam na holim planti hap long Niugini olsem [[Niu Ailan]], [[Manus]], [[Niu Briten]], [[Bogenvil]], Momase Rijen na tu [[Oro]] na [[Milen Be]]. Planti pait i kamap long kainkain hap long kantri long dispela taim. Dispela wo i pinis long 1945. Bihain long wo, Papua na Niugini i pas wantaim olsem wanpela giraun, wantaim nem Papua na Niugini, na Ostrelia i lukautim. Haus bilong Asembli, olsem Palamen, i stat long 1964. Long 1972 nupela ileksen i kamap long Palamen tru, na ol memba i makim [[Michael Somare]] olsem nambawan Praim Minista bilong kantri. Long dispela taim, nem bilong kantri i senis i go long Papua Niugini. Long yia 1975, long 16 Septemba, Papua Niugini i kisim independens long Ostrelia, na em i sanap olsem wanpela kantri em yet nau. Michael Somare bilong [[Pangu Pati]] i stap olsem Praim Minista inap long yia 1980, na long dispela taim Palamen i vot long rausim em na Julius Chan i kisim nambawan sia nau. Long yia 1982, Michael Somare i winim vot na sanap olsem Praim Minista gen, tasol Palamen i rausim em long 1985 na givim dispela posisen i go long Paias Wingti. Wingti i stap yet olsem Praim Minista bihain long ol ileksen bilong yia 1987, tasol Palamen i rausim em long 1988 na makim Rabbie Namaliu. Traipela pait long [[Bogenvil]] i stat long yia 1988 i go long yia 1997. Klostu tupela ten tausen (20,000) manmeri i dai pinis long dispela pait. Long yia 1992, Sir Julius Chan i kisim pawa gen, inap long 1997, taim em i risain bihain long traubel wantaim Sandlain long [[Bogenvil]]. Palamen i makim Bill Skate olsem Praim Minista long dispela taim. Long 1999, oli rausim em gen, na Sir Mekere Morauta em i sanap olsem nupela Praim Minista bilong kantri. Long ileksen bilong yia 2002, nupela pati bilong Sir Michael Somare, Nesenel Alains, i wokim nupela gavman, na long nambawan taim long kantri, dispela gavman istap long faivpela yia inap long ol ileksen long yia 2007. Long nesenel ileksen bilong yia 2007, Nesenel Alains i winim ol narapela pati na kirapim nupela gavman gen. [[Giraun]]. Hekte bilong kantri em i 452,860 km². Papua Niugini i silip antap long Raun bilong Paia bilong Pasifik, na olsem igat planti maunten i save pairap, na tu em i peles bilong ol guria. Long yia 1994 wanpela pairap bilong Tavurvur na Vulcan i bagarapim Rabaul taun olgeta. Ol abus na [[diwai]]. Bigpela hap bilong ol pisin na abus bilong [[Niugini Ailan]] i wanlain long sampela pisin na abus bilong [[Ostrelia]]. Igat tupela bigpela lain bilong ol tokples: ol tokples Papua, na ol tokples Ostronisia. Igat tripela tokples bilong Palamen: Tok Inglis, [[Tok Pisin]] na [[Hiri Motu]], tasol tokples bilong gavman na bigpela hap bilong ol sikul em i Tok Inglis. Sampela sikul i yusim ol lokol tokples wantaim ol yangpela sumatin long halivim ol long lainim pasin bilong ridim na raitim. title: Kamano
text:
Kamano (Kamano-Kafe) em i wanpela tokples long <a href="Isten%20Hailans%20provins">Isten Hailans provins</a> long Papua Niugini. Sampela ol lain i save kolim Kamano olsem tok ples Kafe.
Sen bilong Sentens.
Kamano Kafe i gat wanpela samting long grama bilong en na ol i kolim nem bilong em Sen bilong Sentens. Planti ol lain tok ples Papua i gat grama olsem dispela. Olsem, long tok ples Kamano, taim yu stori, yu mas usim wanpela kain tok bilong wok pastaim na narapela tok bilong wok bihain. Wanpela master i lainim tok ples Kamano na i tok olsem, tok ples Kamano i gat naispela grama olsem, long wanem long tok bilong wok i kamap pastim long stori, dispela tok bilong wok i soim yu husait wokim dispela wok na hamas manmeri i wokim. . Wanpela sentens i kamap hia.

title: Daka
text:
Daka i sayor bilong lain "Piperales". I gat kain kain daka:
Ol i yusim lip bilong daka long kirapim tingting, long kilim jem, na long switim maus. Long <a href="Ayurvedik%20marasin">Ayurvedik marasin</a> ol i yusim bilong kirapim man na meri i laikim. Long Malesia ol i marasinim pen long <a href="het">het</a> na <a href="skru">skru</a>. Long <a href="Tailan">Tailan</a> na <a href="Saina">Saina</a> ol i helpim tit i gat pen. Long <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a> ol i boilim lip na dringim olsem marasin i kilim jem. Na ol i dringim lipwara bilong helpim bel i gat sik, na ol i welim o smelim bilong helpim het i gat pen, o helpim rot bilong pekpek i pulap tumas, o long klinim <a href="nus">nus</a>, o long helpim <a href="susu">susu</a>.

Long Ayurvedik marasin ol i yusim bilong kirapim man na meri i laikim. Long Malesia ol i marasinim pen long het na skru. Long [[Tailan]] na Saina ol i helpim tit i gat pen. Long Indonesia ol i boilim lip na dringim olsem marasin i kilim jem. Na ol i dringim lipwara bilong helpim bel i gat sik, na ol i welim o smelim bilong helpim het i gat pen, o helpim rot bilong pekpek i pulap tumas, o long klinim nus, o long helpim susu.

title: Kaukau
text: Kaukau ("Ipomoea batatas") i stap olsem namba wan kaikai bilong planti manmeri i stap long kain kain hap. Kaukau i no save rausim naitrogen i go aut long graun. Dispela i bikpela samting olsem wanpela i inap plantim planti kaukau na em no bai kilim graun. George Washington Carver, wanpela man bilong Amerika bin mekim planti kain invension yu ken mekim long kaukau.

Dispela i bikpela samting olsem wanpela i inap plantim planti kaukau na em no bai kilim graun. title: Kriol tokples

title: Netirel seleksan
text:
Netirel seleksan (<a href="Tokples%20Inglis">Inglis</a>: natural selection) em i pasin bilong <a href="ivolusan">ivolusan</a>: ol animal na planis senis long bigpela taim, na givim senis long pikinini bilong ol long <a href="DNA">DNA</a>.
Eksempel nambawan:
Sapos mama abus i karim planti pikini, sompela stronpela, arapela nogat, ol strongpela bai stap laif na i gat pikini bilong ol yet, tasol arapela ating bai dai na i no gat pikini: bihain longpela taim, olgeta abus bilong dispela kain strongpela.
Eksempel nambatu:
Ol hos (horses) bilong bifo i stap liklik na igat sotpela lek (saientis painim bun bilong ol pinis). Hos i gat longpela lek mo is save ranawe hariap mo na i stap laif, tasol hos i gat sotpela lek ino nap eskep laian na laian kaikai ol. Bihain longpela taim hos bikam bigpela wantaim longpela lek.
Eksempel namba tripela:
Ol saientis tingting bifo i gat mangi (monkeys). Mangi i nap sanap inap ranawe na usim ol han bilong ol. Ol lainim toktok, wokim paia na wokim bunara na haus bilong ol: ol bikam man meri. 
Sompela lain i no bilipim dispela stori, ol bilipim Baibel na olsem Papa God crietim Adam na Eve na olsem yumi olgeta pikinini bilong Adam na Eve.

title: Barraba
text:
Barraba i viles long Niu Inglan rijon long <a href="Niu%20Saut%20Wels">Niu Saut Wels</a> long <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a>. Bipo viles i bikples bilong distrik "Barraba Shire". Viles na distrik i joinim wantaim distrik bilong Tamworth Regional Council long 2004. Barraba i stap long 'Bikpela Eria bilong ol Balus bilong Bundarra na Barraba'. Dispela eria i sambai bus bilong balus Regent Honeyeater ("Anthochaera phrygia") em i balus no stap tumas.
Barraba i stap 477 kilomita notwes long <a href="Sidni">Sidni</a>, 548 kilomita sautwes long <a href="Brisbin">Brisbin</a>, na 90 kilomita not long <a href="Tamweth">Tamweth</a> em i biktaun klostu winim bilong olgeta.
Wara Manilla i ran arere long viles. Barraba i stap long rot "Fossickers Way" na i stap long ol maunten "Nandewar Range".
Histori.
Manmeri Aborijini, ol Kamilaroi, i stap long ples bipo ol Yuropen i kamap. Namba wan Yuropen em i kam long dispela distrik i Allan Cunningham em i bin kamap long ples long 1827. Em i bin man bilong painim nupela ples na saveman i laik kisim save long ol gutpela diwai bus samting. Ol i kirapim namba wan fam, "Barraba Station", pinis long distrik long 1837 o 1838. Ol i makim ples long viles pinis long 1852.
Painimaut long gol i bin kamapim viles. Ol i kirapim namba wan pos opis pinis long 1856 na ol i kirapim namba wan skul pinis long 1861. Ol i wokim namba wan lotu Angliken pinis long 1876 na ol i kirapim namba wan beng pinis long 1876 tu. Ol i wokim namba wan hotel, "Commercial Hotel", pinis long 1878 na ol i wokim haus kot pinis long 1881. Ol i tokautim Barraba viles long 1885. Ol i wokim haus sik pinis long 1885 na ol i wokim namba wan lotu Metodis pinis long 1898.
Ol i kamapim niuspepa bilong ples, "The Barraba Gazette", long 1900. Ol i wokim lotu <a href="Katolik">Katolik</a> pinis long 1906. Rot bilong tren i kamap long Barraba long 1908 tasol las tren i ran long Barraba long 1983 na ol i rot long tren pasim pinis long 1987. Ol i wokim Banis bilong Wara bilong Connors Creek pinis long 1993 bilong kamapim wara saplai long viles.
Ol main.
Bras.
Ol i painimautim bras (long tok Inglis: copper) pinis long Gulf Creek long 1889 na ol i kirapim namba wan bras main pinis long 1892. Gulf Creek i stap 22 kilomita notis long Barraba. Ol i kirapim liklik viles pinis em i bin gat hotel, skul, na pos opis. Dispela main i bin bras min em i bikpela winim olgeta long Niu Saut Wels bilong 1901 na liklik viles i bin gat 300 manmeri long en. Tasol ol i pasim dispela main pinis long ol yia 1930. Ol i pasim pos opis bilong liklik viles pinis long 1966. Ol i lusim liklik viles pinis.
Asbestos.
Ol i bin main <a href="asbestos">asbestos</a> kirap long 1919 i go inap long 1983 long Woodsreef em i liklik viles stap 15 kilomita is long Barraba. Ol i wokim main i go bikpela moa long 1974. Main i bin wokim 500,000 ton long waitpela asbestos. 
Main i bin lusim 75,000,000 ton long waitpela asbestos na 25,000,000 ton long ol bikpela ston ol i bin no laik. Olgeta asbestos i kamarupim 43 hekta na hip i go inap 70 mita antap.
Long 2008 nius bilong televisen i tok long wari long abestos em i ating mekim sik menmeri bilong Barraba. "Abestos Diseases Foundation of Australia" ol i bin singaut long we gavman mas stretim ples bilong main. Ol i bin singaut long tu nogat manmeri i no inap i go long ples bilong main. Rot i bin go long hap ples bilong main tasol ol i pasim dispela rot pinis long 2013. Ol i lusim liklik viles pinis.
Helt sevis "Hunter-New England Health" i bin mekim stadi long ol problem bilong helt tasol ol i no lusim dispela stadi yet.
Diatomit.
Ol i kirapim diatomit (long Tok Inglis: diatomite o diatomaceous earth) main pinis long 1982. Ol i yusim diatomit bilong wokim ol paura bom, ol pilta, ol polis long rubim, ol poisin bilong kilim i dai ol binatang, ol samting bilong stapim hot o kol i kam insait, long egrikulta, na pasin bilong wokim brik.
Ol ston em ol i pe i antap tru.
Man i inap painim plenti ston em i pe antap tru. Man i inap painim ol piksa bilong ston tu.
Egrikalsa.
Ol fem bilong ples i gat <a href="bulmakau">bulmakau</a> long mit, <a href="sipsip">sipsip</a> long mit na <a href="wul">wul</a>, o <a href="wit">wit</a>.
Taim.
Ol taim bilong biksun long Barraba i hot na i ren. Ol taim bilong kol long Barraba i kol na i drai. De em i bin hot winim bilong olgeta i gat 41.8°C. De em i bin kol winim bilong olgeta i gat -9.4°C. Averes ren bilong wanpela yia i 688 milimita. De em i gat plenti ren i pundaun bilong winim olgeta i 25 Februari 1955. Long dispela de i bin gat 194.3 milimita.
Wara saplai.
Bipo ol i wokim Banis bilong wara ol kolim "Split Rock Dam" pinis, manmeri bilong Barraba i kamautim wara long Banis bilong Wara ol i kolim "Connors Creek Dam", long liklik wara Barraba ("Barraba Creek"), na long wara Manilla. Taim ol dispela as i drai, manmeri bilong Barraba i bin kamautim wara long ol hul wara. 
Ol i wokim Banis bilong wara ol i kolim "Split Rock Dam" pinis long 1988, na ol i wokim bikpela mambu bilong wara pinis kirap long banis bilong wara i go inap long viles long 2015.

Olgeta asbestos i kamarupim 43 hekta na [[hip]] i go inap 70 mita antap. Long 2008 nius bilong televisen i tok long wari long abestos em i ating mekim sik menmeri bilong [[Barraba]]. "Abestos Diseases [[Foundation]] of [[Australia]]" ol i bin singaut long we gavman [[mas]] stretim ples bilong main. [[Ol]] i bin singaut long tu nogat manmeri i no inap i go long ples bilong main. Rot i bin go long hap ples bilong main tasol ol i pasim dispela rot pinis long 2013. Ol i lusim liklik viles pinis. Helt sevis "[[Hunter-New England Health]]" i bin mekim stadi long ol problem bilong helt tasol ol i no lusim dispela stadi yet. Diatomit. Ol i kirapim diatomit (long Tok Inglis: diatomite o diatomaceous earth) main pinis long 1982. Ol i yusim diatomit bilong wokim ol paura bom, ol pilta, ol polis long rubim, ol poisin bilong kilim i dai ol binatang, ol samting bilong stapim hot o kol i kam insait, long egrikulta, na pasin bilong wokim brik. Ol ston em ol i pe i antap tru. [[Man]] i inap painim plenti ston em i pe antap tru. [[Man]] i inap painim ol piksa bilong ston tu. Egrikalsa. Ol fem bilong ples i gat [[bulmakau]] long mit, sipsip long mit na wul, o wit. Taim. Ol taim bilong biksun long Barraba i hot na i ren. Ol taim bilong kol long Barraba i kol na i drai. De em i bin hot winim bilong olgeta i gat 41.8°C. De em i bin kol winim bilong olgeta i gat -9.4°C. Averes ren bilong wanpela yia i 688 milimita. De em i gat plenti ren i pundaun bilong winim olgeta i 25 Februari 1955. Long dispela de i bin gat 194.3 milimita. Wara saplai. Bipo ol i wokim Banis bilong wara ol kolim "Split Rock Dam" pinis, manmeri bilong Barraba i kamautim wara long Banis bilong Wara ol i kolim "Connors Creek Dam", long liklik wara Barraba ("Barraba Creek"), na long wara [[Manilla]]. Taim ol dispela as i drai, manmeri bilong Barraba i bin kamautim wara long ol hul wara.  Ol i wokim Banis bilong wara ol i kolim "Split Rock Dam" pinis long 1988, na ol i wokim bikpela mambu bilong wara pinis kirap long banis bilong wara i go inap long viles long 2015.

title: Sande
text:
Sande i nambaseven de bilong <a href="wik">wik</a>, o de bihain tru bilong wik.
Long sampela kantri (olsem <a href="Yunaitet%20Stet">Amerika</a> na <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a>), wik i stat long <a href="Sande">Sande</a>, na Sande i nambawan de bilong wik.
Nem Sande i kam long Tok Inglis "Sunday". Dispela i min "Sun’s Day", o de bilong San. Bipo bipo tru long <a href="Yurop">Yurop</a>, ol i lotuim san. Ol i tingting san i wanpela masalai, o <a href="got">got</a>.
Long planti kantri ol i no wok long Sande. Sande wantaim <a href="Sarere">Sarere</a> ol i mekim <a href="wiken">wiken</a>, o hap bilong wik i no gat wok.
Long lotu bilong ol <a href="Kristen">Kristen</a>, Sande i de antap bilong lotuim. Planti manmeri bilong Kristen ol i go long <a href="sios">sios</a>, o haus lotu bilong ol Kristen.

title: Tunde
text:
Tunde i nambatu de bilong <a href="wik">wik</a>.
Long sampela kantri (olsem <a href="Amerika">Amerika</a> na <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a>), wik i stat long <a href="Sande">Sande</a>, na Tunde i nambatri de bilong wik.
Nem Tunde i kam long Tok Inglis "Tuesday". Bipo bipo tru, dispela i min "Tew’s Day", o de bilong <a href="masalai">masalai</a>, o <a href="got">got</a>, ol i kolim Tiu o Tir. Em i masalai bilong fait ol i lotuim long dispela taim.
Tasol ating taim <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a> i kirap, manmeri i save toktok long Tok Pisin ol i tingting dispela i min "Two Day", o nambatu de. Na tu, sampela man o meri it tok "de" olsem "nde". Olrait "Tuesday" i kamap Tunde. Nau "nambatri de" em i kamap <a href="trinde">trinde</a>, na "nambafo de" em i kamap <a href="fonde">fonde</a>.

title: Pot Mosbi
text:
Pot Mosbi o Mosbi ("Port Moresby" long <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>) em i wanpela taun long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Em i kapitol bilong kantri, na ol opis bilong nesenal <a href="gavman">gavman</a> i stap long Mosbi. Emi stap insait long <a href="Nesenel%20Kapitol%20Distrik">Nesenel Kapitol Distrik</a> na tu emi kapitol bilong <a href="Sentral%20Provins">Sentral Provins</a>. 
Mosbi em i nambawan bikpela taun bilong Papua Niugini. Long yia <a href="2000">2000</a> 254,158 manmeri i bin stap long Mosbi. Papua Niugini i kamap, na planti manmeri i kam long painim wok long Mosbi. Olgeta niuspepa na television na redio na planti beng na bisnis i stap long Mosbi. Mosbi i gat bikpela wok bilong Papua Niugini istap long en.
Stori bilong taun.
Sampela peles bilong ol Motu na Koitabu pipol i stap pinis long hap bilong Mosbi taun. Bigpela peles bilong ol Motu, klostu tru long <a href="Mosbi%20Taun">Dauntaun</a>, emi <a href="Hanuabada">Hanuabada</a>. Ol Motu lain i save wokim traipela ron wantaim ol bot, oli kolim Hiri, long baim na salim ol samting. Nau yet yumi tingting bek long ol Hiri long wanwan yia long <a href="Hiri%20Moale">Hiri Moale</a> long Septemba long <a href="Ela%20Bis">Ela Bis</a>.
Long yia 1873, wanpela bot bilong Inglan i kam na painim basis long Mosbi na tokaut olsem em bai giraun bilong ol nau. Nem bilong kepten bilong bot emi John Moresby, na emi givim nem "Port Moresby" long tingim papa bilong em, Sir Fairfax Moresby.
Taim wo i stat long 1941, ol ami bilong Amerika na Ostrelia i kam na wokim traipela ami bes long Mosbi. Planti pait i kamap long ol maunten namel long Mosbi na Oro Provins, na tu planti ol manmeri Papua i lusim Mosbi na go bek long ol peles bilong ol long dispela taim.
Bihain long wo, Mosbi i kamap olsem kapitol bilong gavman, na long taim bilong Independens bilong Papua Niugini long 1975, Mosbi emi kisim nem olsem kapitol bilong kantri. Ol i wokim planti nupela bigpela haus bilong gavman, na nupela Haus bilong Palamen i op long 1984.
Long yia 2004, wanpela ripot itok olsem Mosbi emi winim olgeta siti bilong wol olsem emi hap nogut. Oli tok olsem bilong wanem igat planti pasin nogut olsem rep, stilpasin, na kilim ol raskol i save wokim.
Ol liklik hap.
Insait long siti igat planti ol liklik hap. Planti ol bikpela opis istap long <a href="Mosbi%20Taun">Mosbi Taun</a>. Planti ol opis bilong <a href="gavman">gavman</a> na <a href="Palamen">Palamen</a> istap long <a href="Waigani">Waigani</a>. Igat planti bisnis na stua long <a href="Boroko">Boroko</a>. Na tu igat <a href="Tuaguba">Tuaguba</a>, <a href="Koki">Koki</a> (na maket bilong em), <a href="Badili">Badili</a>, <a href="Gabutu">Gabutu</a>, <a href="Konedobu">Konedobu</a>, <a href="Matirogo">Matirogo</a>, <a href="Tri%20Mail">Tri Mail</a>, <a href="Kaugere">Kaugere</a>, <a href="Korobosea">Korobosea</a>, <a href="Fo%20Mail">Fo Mail</a>, <a href="Gordons">Gordons</a> (wantaim bikpela maket), <a href="Erima">Erima</a>, <a href="Hohola">Hohola</a>, <a href="Morata">Morata</a>, <a href="Gerehu">Gerehu</a>, <a href="Faiv%20Mail">Faiv Mail</a>, <a href="Siks%20Mail">Siks Mail</a>, <a href="Et%20Mail">Et Mail</a>, <a href="Nain%20Mail">Nain Mail</a>, na tu ol peles olsem <a href="Hanuabada">Hanuabada</a> bilong ol <a href="Motu">Motu</a> lain.
linked_text: Pot Mosbi o Mosbi ("Port Moresby" long Tok Inglis) em i wanpela taun long [[Papua Niugini]]. Em i kapitol bilong kantri, na ol opis bilong nesenal [[gavman]] i stap long Mosbi. Emi stap insait long [[Nesenel Kapitol Distrik]] na tu emi kapitol bilong [[Sentral Provins]].  Mosbi em i nambawan bikpela taun bilong Papua Niugini. Long yia [[2000]] 254,158 manmeri i bin stap long Mosbi. Papua Niugini i kamap, na planti manmeri i kam long painim wok long Mosbi. Olgeta niuspepa na television na redio na planti beng na bisnis i stap long Mosbi. Mosbi i gat bikpela wok bilong Papua Niugini istap long en. Stori bilong taun. Sampela peles bilong ol Motu na Koitabu pipol i stap pinis long hap bilong Mosbi taun. Bigpela peles bilong ol Motu, klostu tru long Dauntaun, emi Hanuabada. Ol Motu lain i save wokim traipela ron wantaim ol bot, oli kolim Hiri, long baim na salim ol samting. Nau yet yumi tingting bek long ol Hiri long wanwan yia long Hiri Moale long Septemba long Ela Bis. Long yia 1873, wanpela bot bilong [[Inglan]] i kam na painim basis long [[Mosbi]] na tokaut olsem em bai giraun bilong ol nau. Nem bilong kepten bilong bot emi [[John Moresby]], na emi givim nem "[[Port Moresby]]" long tingim [[papa]] bilong em, [[Sir Fairfax Moresby]]. Taim wo i stat long 1941, ol ami bilong [[Amerika]] na [[Ostrelia]] i [[kam]] na wokim traipela ami bes long [[Mosbi]]. Planti pait i kamap long ol maunten namel long [[Mosbi]] na Oro Provins, na tu planti ol manmeri [[Papua]] i lusim [[Mosbi]] na go bek long ol peles bilong ol long dispela taim. Bihain long wo, [[Mosbi]] i kamap olsem kapitol bilong gavman, na long taim bilong Independens bilong [[Papua Niugini]] long 1975, [[Mosbi]] emi kisim nem olsem kapitol bilong kantri. Ol i wokim planti nupela bigpela haus bilong gavman, na nupela Haus bilong Palamen i op long 1984. Long yia 2004, wanpela ripot itok olsem [[Mosbi]] emi winim olgeta siti bilong [[wol]] olsem emi hap nogut. Oli tok olsem bilong wanem igat planti pasin nogut olsem rep, stilpasin, na kilim ol raskol i save wokim. Ol liklik hap. Insait long siti igat planti ol liklik hap. Planti ol bikpela opis istap long Mosbi Taun. Planti ol opis bilong [[gavman]] na Palamen istap long Waigani. Igat planti bisnis na stua long Boroko. Na tu igat Tuaguba, Koki (na maket bilong em), Badili, Gabutu, Konedobu, Matirogo, Tri Mail, Kaugere, Korobosea, Fo Mail, Gordons (wantaim bikpela maket), Erima, Hohola, Morata, Gerehu, Faiv Mail, Siks Mail, Et Mail, Nain Mail, na tu ol peles olsem Hanuabada bilong ol Motu lain.

title: Fraide
text:
Fraide i nambafaiv de bilong <a href="wik">wik</a>.
Long sampela kantri (olsem <a href="Amerika">Amerika</a> na <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a>), wik i stat long <a href="Sande">Sande</a>, na Fraide i nambasikis de bilong wik.
Nem Fraide i kam long Tok Inglis "Friday". Bipo bipo tru, dispela i min "Frige’s Day", o de bilong masalai, o got, ol i kolim Frige. Em i masalai meri bilong pasin laikim, long dispela taim. 
Sapos yumi i gat wok stat Mande i go inap Fraide na yumi i no gat wok long Sarere na Sande, orait <a href="Fraide">Fraide</a> em i de bihain tru long taim wok. Planti man o meri i hamamas long nait bilong Fride bikos ol i no mas i go long wok inap long <a href="Mande">Mande</a>. 
Long <a href="Islam">Islam</a>, o <a href="lotu">lotu</a> bilong ol Mahomet, Fraide i de bilong lotuim insait long haus lotu. Long sampela kantri bilong Islam, olsem <a href="Iran">Iran</a> na <a href="Afganistan">Afganistan</a>, wik i stat long <a href="Sarere">Sarere</a>, na i pinis long Fraide.
Long <a href="Judaisim">Judaisim</a>, o <a href="lotu">lotu</a> bilong ol Juda, <a href="Sabat">Sabat</a>, o de bilong lotuim, em i stat long Fraide long taim san i pundaun, na i pinis long taim san i pundaun long <a href="Sarere">Sarere</a>. 
Long sampela <a href="sosaiti">sosaiti</a>, olsem <a href="Yurop">Yurop</a> na <a href="Amerika">Amerika</a>, sampela man o meri i tingting olsem, sapos de namba 13 bilong <a href="mun">mun</a> i Fraide, em i min olsem kas nogut. Tasol, arapela man o meri ol i tingting, dispela tingting em i <a href="supastisen">supastisen</a>, o tingting giaman bilong taim bipo tru.
linked_text: Fraide i nambafaiv de bilong [[wik]]. Long sampela kantri (olsem [[Amerika]] na [[Inglan]]), wik i stat long [[Sande]], na Fraide i nambasikis de bilong wik. Nem Fraide i [[kam]] long Tok Inglis "Friday". Bipo bipo tru, dispela i min "Frige’s Day", o de bilong masalai, o got, ol i kolim Frige. Em i masalai meri bilong pasin laikim, long dispela taim.  Sapos yumi i gat wok stat Mande i go inap Fraide na yumi i no gat wok long Sarere na Sande, orait [[Fraide]] em i de bihain tru long taim wok. Planti man o meri i hamamas long nait bilong Fride bikos ol i no mas i go long wok inap long [[Mande]].  Long [[Islam]], o [[lotu]] bilong ol Mahomet, Fraide i de bilong lotuim insait long haus lotu. Long sampela kantri bilong Islam, olsem [[Iran]] na Afganistan, wik i stat long [[Sarere]], na i pinis long Fraide. Long [[Judaisim]], o [[lotu]] bilong ol Juda, Sabat, o de bilong lotuim, em i stat long Fraide long taim san i pundaun, na i pinis long taim san i pundaun long [[Sarere]].  Long sampela sosaiti, olsem [[Yurop]] na [[Amerika]], sampela man o meri i tingting olsem, sapos de namba 13 bilong [[mun]] i Fraide, em i min olsem kas nogut. Tasol, arapela man o meri ol i tingting, dispela tingting em i supastisen, o tingting giaman bilong taim bipo tru.

title: Kamikaze
text:
Kamikaze（神風 neim bilong em long tok siapan) minim kami -anutu god kaze -win. As bilong dispela tok i kam long taim iet bipo taim ol kong kong i pait. Pait i bin kamap namel lo ol Mongolien na lo <a href="Siapan">Siapan</a>. Ol i pait 13 hundred pela ia igo. Taim pait i kamap ol siapan i kolostu lus tasol wanpela strong pela win kam na bagarapim ol ami bilong ol Mongolian.
Lo 1940s ol sianpan pait lo big pela <a href="Wold%20Wo%20Tu">Wold Wo Tu</a>. Ol ino poretim ol narapela counrti na pait pait uan taim olgeta lain olsem <a href="Amerika">Amerika</a> na <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> na <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a> na <a href="Pilipin">Pilipin</a> na <a href="China">China</a> na <a href="Koria">Koria</a> na Chaina planti kong kong and Uaitman kantri.
Taim ol siapan i lus na olgeta bullet and gun na soldia bilong ol i pisin na daim ol kisim olgeta yang pela lik lik mangi lo ai skul na lo uni na treinim lo kamap pilot. Taim lo trein pinis ol save kisim uan pela balus na flaim na krasim ol balus bilong ol goes insait lo ol sip lo kilim soldia and sinskim sip blong fait.

title: Gandi
text:
Gandi (Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi), i man bilong kantri <a href="India">India</a>. Em i dai pinis long yia <a href="1947">1947</a>. Em i gat biknem long lotu na long toktok politik long kantri bilong em. Ol i kolim tu "Mahatma". "Mahatma" long tokples bilong India, i minim "man igat bikpela sol".
Taim Gandi i stap long India, kantri <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a> ol i bosim India na sampela ol narapela kantri. Planti manmeri bilong ol dispela kantri, ol i laik kamapim independens: ol i laikim bosim kantri bilong ol yet.
Gandi i bin bikpela lida bilong muvmen igo long independens long India. Em i bin yusim "ahimsa", o pasim bilong abrusim pait. Dispela i minim olsem manmeri ol i traim lon wokim senis long kantri bilong ol, tasol ol i no yusim pasin bilong pait, o ol i no bagarapim narapela manmeri o tingting i bilong narapela manmeri.

Planti manmeri bilong ol dispela kantri, ol i laik kamapim independens: ol i laikim bosim kantri bilong ol yet. [[Gandi]] i bin bikpela lida bilong muvmen igo long independens long [[India]]. Em i bin yusim "ahimsa", o pasim bilong abrusim pait. Dispela i minim olsem manmeri ol i traim lon wokim senis long kantri bilong ol, tasol ol i no yusim pasin bilong pait, o ol i no bagarapim narapela manmeri o tingting i bilong narapela manmeri.

title: Bogenvil
text:
Not Solomons o Bogenvil () em i wanpela <a href="provins">provins</a> bilong <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Bogenvil provins nau igat sipesol sindaun olsem ol manmeri bilong provins i bosim sampela ol samting bilong gavman bilong provins ol yet. Igat nem "otonomos" provins () bilong dispela, na nem tru bilong Bogenvil nau emi otonomos region bilong Bogenvil. <a href="Buka">Buka</a> em i kapitol na taun bikpela tumas bilong em, tasol pastaim long pait <a href="Arawa">Arawa</a> emi bin kapitol bilong provins, na nau tu gavman bilong provins itok olsem kapitol bai surik i go long <a href="Arawa">Arawa</a> taun gen.
Long <a href="1966">1966</a>, ol i painim planti <a href="gol">gol</a> long <a href="Panguna">Panguna</a> main, tasol planti manmeri i kamap belhat long wanem kampani i rausim planti gol i go na i no givim planti mani long ol lain bilong ples. Olsem na <a href="Francis%20Ona">Francis Ona</a> i statim <a href="Bogenvil%20Revoluseneri%20Ami">Bogenvil Revoluseneri Ami</a> o BRA, na long <a href="1988">1988</a> ol i kirapim pait wantaim gavman bilong Papua Niugini. Ol i laik lusim PNG na kamap <a href="kantri">kantri</a> bilong ol yet. Dispela pait i pinis long <a href="1997">1997</a> tasol samting olsem 20,000 manmeri i dai pinis long dispela pait.
Long yia <a href="2005">2005</a> igat nambawan ileksen long gavman bilong Bogenvil yet. Ileksen i makim <a href="Joseph%20Kabui">Joseph Kabui</a> olsem nambawan Presiden bilong Bogenvil provins. 
Ol distrik bilong Bogenvil: <a href="Buin">Buin</a>, <a href="Siwai">Siwai</a>, <a href="Bana">Bana</a>, <a href="Kieta">Kieta</a>, <a href="Torokina">Torokina</a>, <a href="Wakunai">Wakunai</a>, <a href="Tinputz">Tinputz</a>, <a href="Weskos">Weskos</a>, <a href="Buka">Buka</a>, <a href="Atolls">Atolls</a>, na <a href="Nissan">Nissan</a>.

Igat nem "otonomos" provins () bilong dispela, na nem tru bilong Bogenvil nau emi otonomos region bilong Bogenvil. [[Buka]] em i kapitol na taun bikpela tumas bilong em, tasol pastaim long pait [[Arawa]] emi bin kapitol bilong provins, na nau tu gavman bilong provins itok olsem kapitol bai surik i go long [[Arawa]] taun gen. Long [[1966]], ol i painim planti gol long [[Panguna]] main, tasol planti manmeri i kamap belhat long wanem kampani i rausim planti gol i go na i no givim planti mani long ol lain bilong ples. Olsem na Francis Ona i statim Bogenvil Revoluseneri Ami o BRA, na long [[1988]] ol i kirapim pait wantaim gavman bilong Papua Niugini. Ol i laik lusim PNG na kamap [[kantri]] bilong ol yet. title: Famili
text:
Kainkain lain i gat kainkain famili. Long Yurop ol manmeri i sindaun wantaim mamapapa na pikinini long en tasol. Bipo, ol lain Yurop i sindaun long wanpela haus wantaim mamapapa, pikinini, ol mamapapa long mamapapa, braadasusa long en, na bikpela famili i stap wantaim. Long wanim, ol i mas lukautim planti samtin wantaim- ol meri i wok long haus, na ol man i wok long gaden o long bisnis blong en. Nau, i gat planti kainkain famili long Yurop. Meri tasol i sindaun wantaim pikinini bilong en o man tasol wantaim pikinini bilong en. Sapos mamapapa indai pinis, pikinini bilong ol i stap long narapela lain i lukautim en. Sapos mamapapa i save bagarapim pikini na paitim ol, ol lain gavman i tekawe pikini bilong ol nogut lain na givim em long arapela manmeri i mas lukautim gut long en. 
Olgeta kainkain lain i gat narapela kain famili, tasol olgeta famiii i gat pasin bilong lukautim meri na pikinini. Long wanwan kantri, ol man i no save sindaun wantaim meri bilong en long wanpela haus- ol brada bilong meri i lukautim dispela meri na pikinini bilong en. Long arapela lain, man i gat planti meri na planti pikinini. Arapela lain tude i no save karim pikinini, longwanim ol i no laik kirapim planti manmeri tumas long Graun. Long PNG famili bilong manmeri i tu lain bilong asples na wantok bilong en.

title: Panama
text:
Panama emi wanpela kantri bilong <a href="Sentrel%20Amerika">Sentrel Amerika</a>. Klaimat bilong Panama tropical, tasol i gat moa ren long hap bilon Atlantic olsem long hap bilong Pacific. Kapitol siti i stap long hap bilong Pacific, wet sison i kamap long mun June-September nambaut. Siti i gat liklik nesenel park, nem bilong em Parque Natural Metropolitano. Panama i gat bigpela <a href="biodaivesiti">biodaivesiti</a>, i gat plenti kain diwai na pisin na binatang, na tupela kain <a href="slip%20kapul">slip kapul</a>.
Bifo Panama emi wanpela hap bilong kantri <a href="Kolambia">Kolambia</a>, tasol ol American i halivim ol kisim indipendens long yia 1904. Bihain indipendens ol i bin katim traipela sotkat bilong ol bot, nem bilong em Panama Canal. Nau ol bot ikam long solwara Atlantic nap go long Canal long solwara Pacific, na ol i sevim bigpela taim.
Ol American i atakim Panama long yia 1989 na rausim dikteta Manuel Noriega na tromwe em long kalabus. Nau i gat <a href="demokrasi">demokrasi</a>, presiden i stap faivpela yia tasol na em i no nap sev tupela taim stret (em mas wet wanpela taim bifo em nap run gen long ilekshan).

title: Tru Jisas Lotu
text:
Tru Jisas Lotu emi wanpela independen <a href="Lotu%20Kristen">Lotu Kristen</a> <a href="sios">sios</a> i kirap long <a href="Beijing">Beijing</a>, <a href="Republik%20bilong%20Manmeri%20bilong%20China">Saina</a>, long 1917. Nau igat olsem 2.5 milien manmeri i save bihainim dispela lotu long 45 kantri istap long sikis kontinen. Sios emi stap long han bilong ol <a href="Pentekostal">Pentekostal</a> lain bilong ol kristen. Tru Jisas Lotu emi bihainim wanpela pasin oli kolim "wanbel Pentekostal pasin - skul bilong nem bilong Jisas" (Tok Inglis: "Oneness Pentecostal theology - Jesus-Name doctrine"). Dispela sios i stat long <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> long yia 1982. Oli tok olsem oli laik bringim gospel long olgeta kantri pastaim long taim bilong Jisas bai kamap gen.
Dispela sios igat tenpela bilip na pasin:
