title: Budisim
text:
Budisim em <a href="lotu">lotu</a> bilong ol Buda. <a href="Sidarta">Sidarta</a>, o <a href="Buda">Buda</a>, em i kirapim budisim long India 2500 yia bipo. Tede i gat 300 milion samting man o meri i lotuim Buda long Graun. 
Histori long Budisim.
Budisim igat longpela histori bilong em. Bihain <a href="Sidarta">Sidarta</a> i bin dai, ol manmeri bilong lotu bilong Sidarta i raitim pinis ol tok bilong Sidarta na em i bin foundation long budisim.
Tok bilong Buda.
Tok bilong <a href="Sidarta">Sidarta</a> em i as bilong budisim. Sidarta i bin tok planti stori na toksave. Tasol tok bikpela tumas tru em i olsem: 
Rot Igat Etpela Han.
Em i etpela pasin yumi i mas bihainim long rausim pen bilong laip: 
Narapela tingting bilong budisim.
<a href="Meditesen">Meditesen</a> em i bikpela samting long lotu budisim. 
Manmeri bilong Buda ol i tok tu olsem: 
Ol Faipela Lo.
Man o meri bilong Buda i mas bihainim dispela faipela lo:

title: Kuala Lumpur
text:
Kuala Lumpur, em i narapela nem KL, em i kapitol bilong <a href="Malaysia">Malesia</a> na em i ples long moa tru manmeri long Malesia. 
Kuala Lumpur em i asples bilong parlemen bilong Malesia na bin asples bilong gavman long Malesia. Ples bilong gavman nau long <a href="Putrajaya">Putrajaya</a>. Em i "alpha world city" na nambawan hap long sosaiti na bisnis long Malesia. Kuala Lumpur em i namba 67 long siti long wol long ekonomiks na sosial "innovation" long yia 2010.
Kuala Lumpur bin ples long <a href="1998%20Commonwealth%20Games">1998 Commonwealth Games</a> na <a href="Formula%20One">Formula One</a> Grand Prix.

title: Siaman Niugini
text:
Siaman Niugini (, ) emi nem bilong noten hap bilong Papua Niugini, taim ol man bilong <a href="Siamani">Siamani</a> i bosim. 
I stat long yia <a href="1883">1883</a>, taim wanpela kampani Siaman Niugini Kampani i kam long Rabaul na stat wokim ol plentesen long <a href="Niu%20Briten">Niu Briten</a>, <a href="Niu%20Ailan">Niu Ailan</a>, <a href="Bogenvil">Bogenvil</a> na <a href="Momase%20Rijen">Momase Rijen</a>. Long dispela taim, kampani emi olsem wanpela gavman bilong hap. 
Long yia <a href="1899">1899</a>, gavman bilong Siamani i kam na tokim kampani olsem gavman yet bai bosim nau. 
Long yia <a href="1914">1914</a>, ami bilong <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> i kam na rausim ol lain bilong gavman bilong Siamani, na gavman bilong Ostrelia i bosim dispela hap nau inap long independens bilong Papua Niugini long yia <a href="1975">1975</a>.
linked_text: Siaman Niugini (, ) emi nem bilong noten hap bilong Papua Niugini, taim ol man bilong [[Siamani]] i bosim.  I stat long yia 1883, taim wanpela kampani Siaman Niugini Kampani i kam long Rabaul na stat wokim ol plentesen long [[Niu Briten]], [[Niu Ailan]], [[Bogenvil]] na Momase Rijen. Long dispela taim, kampani emi olsem wanpela gavman bilong hap.  Long yia 1899, gavman bilong Siamani i kam na tokim kampani olsem gavman yet bai bosim nau.  Long yia [[1914]], ami bilong [[Ostrelia]] i kam na rausim ol lain bilong gavman bilong Siamani, na gavman bilong Ostrelia i bosim dispela hap nau inap long independens bilong Papua Niugini long yia [[1975]].

title: Biodaivesiti
text:
Biodaivesiti (Tok Inglis: Biodiversity) em i namba long enimol na planis long wanpela ples o kantri.
Edward O. Wilson i inventim dispela tok na olgeta yusim em nau bicos yumi olgeta mas sevim biodaivesiti: noken kilim olgeta enimol, noken katim olgeta diwai, noken bagarapim graun.
Biodaivesiti risolt bilong <a href="ivolusan">ivolusan</a>.
<a href="Larry%20Orsak">Larry Orsak</a> i bin stadi na lukautim biodaivesiti bilong Papua New Guinea.

title: Unserdeutsch
text:
Unserdeutsch ("Siaman bilong yumi" long <a href="Tok%20Jeman">Tok Jeman</a>) o Kriol Siaman bilong Rabaul, emi wanpela tokples istap pinis long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. As tokples bilong en emi Tok Jeman. Ananit long 100 manmeri i save long dispela tokples nau, na olsem 15 bilong ol istap long <a href="Niu%20Briten">Niu Briten</a>. Long taim bifo igat sampela manmeri long noten hap bilong Ostrelia i save long dispela tokples.
Ol manmeri husat i save long Unserdeutsch ol i save long tupela tokples o antap; ol i save long <a href="Tok%20Jeman">Tok Jeman</a>, <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>, <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a> o <a href="Kuanua">Kuanua</a>. Bikpela hap bilong ol manmeri husat i save long dispela tokples oli lapun liklik nau. 
Dispela tokples i stat long taim bilong <a href="Siaman%20Niugini">Siaman Niugini</a>, long <a href="Is%20Niu%20Briten">Is Niu Briten</a>, namel long ol pikinini Tolai i no gat papamama na ol Saiman sista bilong sios i lukautim. Bihain long taim bilong Siaman Niugini, na wantaim ol senis we ol manmeri i save raun long ol hap bilong Papua Niugini na long wol, na marit long ol narapela hap, dispela tokples i go daun, na nau i no gat planti manmeri i save long en.
Sampela hap tok long Unserdeutsch i go insait long Tok Pisin pinis. Ol manmeri husat i save long Tok Jeman inap harim Unserdeutsch na save long en.
linked_text: Unserdeutsch ("Siaman bilong yumi" long [[Tok Jeman]]) o Kriol Siaman bilong Rabaul, emi wanpela tokples istap pinis long [[Papua Niugini]]. As tokples bilong en emi Tok Jeman. Ananit long 100 manmeri i save long dispela tokples nau, na olsem 15 bilong ol istap long [[Niu Briten]]. Long taim bifo igat sampela manmeri long noten hap bilong Ostrelia i save long dispela tokples. Ol manmeri husat i save long Unserdeutsch ol i save long tupela tokples o antap; ol i save long [[Tok Jeman]], Tok Inglis, [[Tok Pisin]] o Kuanua. Bikpela hap bilong ol manmeri husat i save long dispela tokples oli lapun liklik nau.  Dispela tokples i stat long taim bilong [[Siaman Niugini]], long [[Is Niu Briten]], namel long ol pikinini Tolai i no gat papamama na ol Saiman sista bilong sios i lukautim. Bihain long taim bilong Siaman Niugini, na wantaim ol senis we ol manmeri i save raun long ol hap bilong Papua Niugini na long wol, na marit long ol narapela hap, dispela tokples i go daun, na nau i no gat planti manmeri i save long en. Sampela hap tok long Unserdeutsch i go insait long Tok Pisin pinis. Ol manmeri husat i save long Tok Jeman inap harim Unserdeutsch na save long en.

title: Save long komputa
text:
Komputa o hetbokis o tingtingbokis (<a href="Tokples%20Inglis">Inglis</a>:computer) emi wanpela kain mesin i nap tingting na tingim, olsem het bilong man.
Long usim komputa yumi olgeta mas givim toksave long em, ol i kolim progremim komputa (Inglis: to program). 
Save long wokim na progremim komputa ol i kolim "save long komputa" (Inglis: computer science).
I gat planti tokples ol hetbokis inap harim: Java, JavaScript, C, C++, PHP, Pascal, Scheme, Fortran.

title: Disemba
text:
Disemba i <a href="mun">mun</a> namba wanpela ten tu bilong <a href="yia">yia</a> long <a href="Kalenda%20Pop%20Gregori">Kalenda Pop Gregori</a>. 
Dispela mun i gat 31 <a href="de">de</a>, olsem <a href="Janueri">Janueri</a>, <a href="Mas">Mas</a>, <a href="Me">Me</a>, <a href="Julai">Julai</a>, <a href="Ogas">Ogas</a>, <a href="Oktoba">Oktoba</a>. 
Nem Disemba i kam long Decem, i min "namba ten" long <a href="tok%20Latin">tok Latin</a>, olsem wanem dispela Mun i bin Mun namba ten long kalenda bilong ol <a href="Roma">Roma</a>, taim bipo tru. 
Long <a href="tok%20Inglis">tok Inglis</a>: "December".
linked_text: Disemba i [[mun]] namba wanpela ten tu bilong [[yia]] long Kalenda Pop Gregori.  Dispela mun i gat 31 [[de]], olsem [[Janueri]], [[Mas]], [[Me]], [[Julai]], [[Ogas]], [[Oktoba]].  Nem Disemba i kam long Decem, i min "namba ten" long [[tok Latin]], olsem wanem dispela Mun i bin Mun namba ten long kalenda bilong ol Roma, taim bipo tru.  Long tok Inglis: "December".

title: Demokrasi
text:
Demokrasi emi wanpela political sistem we ol man meri i gat pawa.
I gat presiden na paliamen i gat posibiliti rausim presiden sapos em i no wokim wok bilong em. Inap rausim memba bilong parliamen tu.
Sapos kantri i no gat demokrasi, ol i kolim presiden bilong kantri <a href="dikteta">dikteta</a>.

title: Is Sepik
text:
Is Sepik () em i wanpela provins long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Dispela provins em i kisim nem long bikpela wara <a href="Sepik">Sepik</a> i ran namel long en. Klostu long solwara, i gat sampela rot olsem rot i lusim <a href="Wewak">Wewak</a> i go long <a href="Aitape">Aitape</a> na <a href="Vanimo">Vanimo</a>, tasol namel long provins, planti bikpela tais i stap na mekim hat long wokim rot, olsem na ol manmeri long hap i save yusim ol kanu na bot long raunraun.
Wewak em i <a href="kapitol">kapitol</a> na bikpela taun tumas bilong provins.

title: Not Koria
text:
Not Korea, o Demokratik Ripablik bilong ol Manmeri bilong Korea (<a href="Tok%20Korea">Tok Korea</a>: 조선민주주의인민공화국) emi wanpela <a href="kantri">kantri</a> long <a href="Esia">Esia</a>. <a href="Saut%20Korea">Saut Korea</a> emi stap long sauten sait bilong en, na long noten sait igat <a href="Saina">Saina</a> na <a href="Rasia">Rasia</a>. 
<a href="Kapitol">Kapitol</a> bilong Not Korea emi <a href="Pyongyang">Pyongyang</a>.
Tokples bilong Not Korea i <a href="Tok%20Korea">Tok Korea</a>.
Stat long yia <a href="1947">1947</a> inap long nau, <a href="Pati%20bilong%20ol%20Wokman%20bilong%20Korea">Pati bilong ol Wokman bilong Korea</a> ol i save bosim Not Korea. <a href="Kim%20Il-Sung">Kim Il-Sung</a> emi Presiden long yia <a href="1947">1947</a> inap long yia <a href="1994">1994</a>, na <a href="Kim%20Jung-Il">Kim Jung-Il</a> emi bikman bilong Kaunsil bilong Dipens long Kantri long yia <a href="1994">1994</a> inap long nau.
linked_text: Not Korea, o Demokratik Ripablik bilong ol Manmeri bilong Korea (Tok Korea: 조선민주주의인민공화국) emi wanpela [[kantri]] long [[Esia]]. Saut Korea emi stap long sauten sait bilong en, na long noten sait igat Saina na [[Rasia]].  [[Kapitol]] bilong Not Korea emi [[Pyongyang]]. Tokples bilong Not Korea i Tok Korea. Stat long yia [[1947]] inap long nau, Pati bilong ol Wokman bilong Korea ol i save bosim Not Korea. Kim Il-Sung emi Presiden long yia [[1947]] inap long yia [[1994]], na Kim Jung-Il emi bikman bilong Kaunsil bilong Dipens long Kantri long yia [[1994]] inap long nau.

title: Goran Švob
text:
Goran Švob (<a href="Zagreb">Zagreb</a>, <a href="Me">Me</a> 29 <a href="1947">1947</a> - <a href="Epril">Epril</a> 18 <a href="2013">2013</a>) i bin man bilong <a href="pilosopi">pilosopi</a> na <a href="lajik">lajik</a> long <a href="Krowesia">Krowesia</a>.
Wok.
Mama i karim em long Me 29, yia 1947 long <a href="Zagreb">Zagreb</a>, wanpela taun long <a href="Krowesia">Krowesia</a>.
Em i bin stadim <a href="pilosopi">pilosopi</a> na <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>. Em i kamap tisa long <a href="1971">1971</a> na em i bin bos long <a href="lajik">lajik</a> long Pakulti bilong pilosopi long Zagreb. Em i bin dokta save long pilosopi (yia <a href="1988">1988</a>, long <a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>: "Fregeovo pojmovno pismo i zasnivanje moderne logike", <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "Frege's Begriffsschrift and the foundation of modern logic", <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a>: "Begriffsschrift bilong Frege na as long nupela lajik"). Em i stadim <a href="Tok%20Saina">Tok Saina</a> na <a href="Tok%20Siapan">Tok Siapan</a>. Long yia <a href="1973">1973</a> na <a href="1974">1974</a> i bin lusim Krowesia na i go long <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a>, long <a href="Oxford">Oxford</a>.
Em i laikim <a href="Gottlob%20Frege">Gottlob Frege</a>, <a href="Bertrand%20Russell">Bertrand Russell</a> na <a href="Ludwig%20Wittgenstein">Ludwig Wittgenstein</a>. Tingting bilong em igat planti respekt long stadi long <a href="pilosopi">pilosopi</a>, <a href="pilosopi%20long%20tokples">pilosopi long tokples</a>, <a href="lajik">lajik</a> na <a href="Tok%20Saina">Tok Saina</a> na <a href="Tok%20Siapan">Tok Siapan</a>. 
Em i dai pinis long Epril 18, 2013 long Zagreb. 
Ol buk na pepa bilong em.
Goran Švob i raitim pinis planti <a href="buk">buk</a>. Buk bilong em i:
Em i raitim plani pepa long save (<a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>, <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>, <a href="Tok%20Saina">Tok Saina</a> na moa).
linked_text: Goran Švob (Zagreb, [[Me]] 29 [[1947]] - [[Epril]] 18 2013) i bin man bilong [[pilosopi]] na [[lajik]] long [[Krowesia]]. Wok. Mama i karim em long Me 29, yia 1947 long Zagreb, wanpela taun long [[Krowesia]]. Em i bin stadim [[pilosopi]] na Tok Inglis. Em i kamap tisa long [[1971]] na em i bin bos long [[lajik]] long Pakulti bilong pilosopi long Zagreb. Em i bin dokta save long pilosopi (yia [[1988]], long [[Tok Krowesia]]: "Fregeovo pojmovno pismo i zasnivanje moderne logike", Tok Inglis: "Frege's Begriffsschrift and the foundation of modern logic", [[Tok Pisin]]: "Begriffsschrift bilong Frege na as long nupela lajik"). Em i stadim [[Tok Saina]] na Tok Siapan. Long yia [[1973]] na [[1974]] i bin lusim Krowesia na i go long [[Inglan]], long Oxford. Em i laikim Gottlob Frege, Bertrand Russell na Ludwig Wittgenstein. Tingting bilong em igat planti respekt long stadi long [[pilosopi]], pilosopi long tokples, [[lajik]] na [[Tok Saina]] na Tok Siapan.  Em i dai pinis long Epril 18, 2013 long [[Zagreb]].  Ol buk na pepa bilong em. Goran Švob i raitim pinis planti [[buk]]. Buk bilong em i: Em i raitim plani pepa long save ([[Tok Krowesia]], Tok Inglis, [[Tok Saina]] na moa).

title: Larry Orsak
text:
Larry Orsak (1953-2017) saientis bilong Amerika, speselist bilong bataplai. Mama i karim em long USA long 15 oktoba 1953. Em stadi na wokim PhD long Kaliponia long 1988.
Em i wok planti yia long Papua Niugini, fes long Wau (<a href="Morobe">Morobe</a> Provins) na bihain long <a href="Madang">Madang</a> na <a href="Lae">Lae</a>. Em wokim bigpela wok long sevim na lukautim <a href="biodaivesiti">biodaivesiti</a> (ol kain diwai na plaua na pisin na binatang) bilong Papua New Guinea. Em halivim sevim bigpela bus long Baitabag viles na wokim wantaim ol lain bilong viles. <a href="Philippe%20Cu%C3%A9noud">Philippe Cuénoud</a> wokim sompela stadi wantaim em long ol bataplai i luk olsem spaida (spider mimicry). Ol i no pablisim dispela stadi, tasol Larry Orsak pablisim long "spider mimicry" bifo . 
Em stat wok long Unitech (Lae) long 2011, na halivim planti studen long PNG. Em kisim studen bilong PNG long USA na soim ol kantri bilong em yet. Em wok planti na slip liklik.
Em dai pinis long Papua Niugini long hatpen (heart attack) long 6 julai 2017. Ol planim em long Baitabag viles, klostu long ol wantok na pren bilong em.
linked_text: [[Larry]] Orsak (1953-2017) saientis bilong [[Amerika]], speselist bilong bataplai. Mama i karim em long [[USA]] long 15 oktoba 1953. Em stadi na wokim PhD long Kaliponia long 1988. Em i wok planti yia long Papua Niugini, fes long Wau ([[Morobe]] Provins) na bihain long Madang na [[Lae]]. Em wokim bigpela wok long sevim na lukautim [[biodaivesiti]] (ol kain diwai na plaua na pisin na binatang) bilong Papua New Guinea. Em halivim sevim bigpela bus long Baitabag viles na wokim wantaim ol lain bilong viles. [[Philippe Cuénoud]] wokim sompela stadi wantaim em long ol bataplai i luk olsem spaida (spider mimicry). Ol i no pablisim dispela stadi, tasol Larry Orsak pablisim long "spider mimicry" bifo .  Em stat wok long Unitech (Lae) long 2011, na halivim planti studen long [[PNG]]. Em kisim studen bilong [[PNG]] long [[USA]] na soim ol kantri bilong em yet. Em wok planti na slip liklik. Em dai pinis long [[Papua Niugini]] long hatpen (heart attack) long 6 julai 2017. Ol planim em long Baitabag viles, klostu long ol wantok na pren bilong em.

title: Hiri Motu
text:
Hiri Motu em i wanpela tokples long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Em i wanpela tok namel i save helpim manmeri long toktok wantaim ol lain i gat narapela as tokples.
Em i wanpela namba tu tokples long Papua Niugini. Planti manmeri long hap saut i gat save long dispela kain tokples. Ofisel tok stret em i Tok Inglis, tasol nogat planti manmeri i stap long ples na save long Inglis. Olsem, na i gat tupela namba tu (seken) ofisel tok long Papua Niugini, tok i gat planti manmeri save long en. Motu, dispela pes i tok long en, na <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a>. Motu em i toktok long hap Papua, na Tok Pisin em i bilong Niugini na Hailans tu.
Planti manmeri stret long Pot Mosbi na sampela arapela hap i gat save long dispela tokples, na planti manmeri long nambis em i gat save long dispela kain tokples, tasol sampela long Not Cos na arapela ples nambis nogat save, na manmeri long highlands ol i nogat save long dispela kain tokples.pls help me

title: Meditesen
text:
Meditesen em i pasin bilong tingting. Kainkain meditesen i kamap long taim bipo tru, i stap long olgeta hap long graun na i gat kainkain mining bilongen. Long sampela hap, meditesen em i as bilong lotu bilongen. Long narapela hap, olsem Amerika o Western kantri, meditesen em i pasin bilong helt. 
Meditesen i kam long <a href="India">India</a> long taim bipo tru. Em i bikpela samting long ol lotu i kam long India, olsem <a href="yoga">yoga</a>, na <a href="Hinduisim">Hinduisim</a> o lotu bilong Hindu, na <a href="budisim">budisim</a> o lotu bilong Buda. Long dispela lotu, meditesen em i wanpela pasin bilong lusim wol. Lusim em i bikpela wok bilong dispela bilip. Man i gat tumas laik bilong tingting bilong wol, i mas lusim dispela laik. Laik bilong gutpela kaikai, laik bilong nupela siot o trausis o redio o wanem, em i nogut tingting bilong manmeri Buda na ol i wok long meditesen long lusim dispela laik. Sapos yu wokim meditesen bilong lotu bilong Buda, maebi yu sindaun long hap, noken toktok, noken tingting, yu pulim win isi isi tasol. Lotu bilong Buda bilip bilongen olsem meditesen i givim hamamas na gutpela sindaun long manmeri i wok hatpela longen, na narapela bilip bilongen olsem meditesen i soim as tru bilong laip long manmeri i wok hatpela hatpela nogut tru longen. Sampela man o meri i no bilong Hindu na i no bilong Buda ol i wokim pasin meditesen tu, bikos em i save mekim bel isi, na rausim kros na fret.
Pasin bilong meditesen i go long olgeta hap long wol na mining bilongen i senis. Long Amerika na Western kantri, pasin bilong meditesen em i olsem kain pasin bilong mekim bel isi tasol na liklik sampela manmeri i bilip long lotu bilong Buda. Sampela dokta i tok olsem meditesen em i pasin bilong mekim bel isi tasol, lotu maski. Narapela sampela dokta i tok olsem olgeta lotu i gat sampela pasin olosem meditesen.

title: Indo-Yuropien famili bilong tokples
text:
Indo-Yuropien famili bilong tokples emi wanpela bikpela <a href="famili%20bilong%20tokples">famili bilong tokples</a> long <a href="Graun">Graun</a>. Planti tokples bilong <a href="Yurop">Yurop</a>, <a href="Rasia">Rasia</a>, <a href="India">India</a> na <a href="Iran">Iran</a> istap long dispela famili. Igat planti liklik famili insait long em.
I gat planti mo liklik famili bilong tokples ol i dai bipo tu. 
<a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a>, <a href="Bislama">Bislama</a> na <a href="Pijin">Pijin</a> igat planti hap tok bilong <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a> tasol ol i no tokples bilong dispela famili. Ol i <a href="tokples%20Pisin">tokples Pisin</a> o <a href="Kriol">Kriol</a>.

Igat planti liklik famili insait long em. I gat planti mo liklik famili bilong tokples ol i dai bipo tu. title: Niugini

Ol hap bilong politikis.
Niugini em i haphapim long klostu long tupela stret hap long lain bilong not-saut:
Ol manmeri.

text: Nesenel Plak blong Filipin (Tok Tagalog: Pambansang Watawat ng Pilipinas) em i stret plak wantaim tupla color, em i blu, ret, na wait, na i gat stret triangle long hoist sait . Long namel blong triangle, gol san i kisim etpla lain na mining blong en i etpla provins blong Filipin husat long taim bipo i bin wokim pait blong gavman blong Spen husat i kisim Filipin blong en. Tripla star, em i tripla ailan blong Filipin, emi ol Luzon ailan, ol Visayas ailan, na ol Mindanao ailan. Wanpla samting Filipin plak i kisim em tasol, em i, sapos taim blong pait i kamap, retpla hap blong plak i go antap.

title: Malesia
text:
Malesia, (tu nem bilong Malaysia) emi wanpela kantri stap long Southeast <a href="Esia">Esia</a>. Emi federation long 13 stet na 3 nesenal teritori. Emi brukim namel tu pat long <a href="South%20China%20Sea">South China Sea</a>. Bikpela hap long hapailan, <a href="Malay%20Peninsula">Malay Peninsula</a> klosap <a href="Straits%20of%20Malacca">Straits of Malacca</a> long wes, na klosap South China Sea long es. Narapela hap bilong kantri stap long north long <a href="ailan">ailan</a> long <a href="Borneo">Borneo</a>, wes long not Philippines i stap klostu (<a href="Palawan">Palawan</a> ailan). Emi nem bilong kapitol <a href="Kuala%20Lumpur">Kuala Lumpur</a>. Nesenal kapitol i bin muv long nupela bikpela taun long Putrajaya. Nupela taun i bin disain long administresen long kantri. 
Gavman sistem bilong Malesia wankain Westminster parlemen sistem. Lo sistem bilong Malesia i inap klostu wankain sistem bilong Britain long 'common law'. Malesia gat planti res na kalsa na lotu. Mo tru manmeri bilong Malay res, tasol long hap Chinese res na Indian res (long India). Opisal tok ples emi stap Tok Malei (Bahasa Melayu) tasol planti pipel bilong Malesia i save Tok Inglis tu.
Opisal lotu bilong Malesia emi stap Islam tasol arapela man o meri bilong kantri inap gat narakain lotu.
linked_text: Malesia, (tu nem bilong Malaysia) emi wanpela kantri stap long Southeast [[Esia]]. Emi federation long 13 stet na 3 nesenal teritori. Emi brukim namel tu pat long South China Sea. Bikpela hap long hapailan, Malay Peninsula klosap Straits of Malacca long wes, na klosap South China Sea long es. Narapela hap bilong kantri stap long north long [[ailan]] long [[Borneo]], wes long not Philippines i stap klostu ([[Palawan]] ailan). Emi nem bilong kapitol [[Kuala Lumpur]]. Nesenal kapitol i bin muv long nupela bikpela taun long Putrajaya. Nupela taun i bin disain long administresen long kantri.  Gavman sistem bilong [[Malesia]] wankain Westminster parlemen sistem. Lo sistem bilong [[Malesia]] i inap klostu wankain sistem bilong [[Britain]] long 'common law'. [[Malesia]] gat planti res na kalsa na lotu. [[Mo]] tru manmeri bilong Malay res, tasol long hap Chinese res na Indian res (long [[India]]). Opisal tok ples emi stap Tok Malei (Bahasa Melayu) tasol planti pipel bilong [[Malesia]] i save Tok Inglis tu. title: Ranko Matasović
text:
Ranko Matasović (<a href="Mei">Mei</a> 14, <a href="1968">1968</a>) em i <a href="man">man</a> bilong <a href="Krowesia">Krowesia</a>. Em i bikpela long <a href="histori">histori</a> long <a href="lingwistikis">lingwistikis</a>. Em i stadim <a href="Indo-Yuropien%20famili%20bilong%20tokples">Indo-Yuropien famili bilong tokples</a> na em i lukluk histori bilong <a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>, <a href="Baltik%20famili%20bilong%20tokples">Baltik famili bilong tokples</a>, <a href="Slavik%20famili%20bilong%20tokples">Slavik famili bilong tokples</a>, <a href="Keltik%20famili%20bilong%20tokples">Keltik famili bilong tokples</a> na mo tokples long <a href="Kokesen">Kokesen</a>.
Wok.
Em i man bilong <a href="Zagreb">Zagreb</a>. Em i bin stadim <a href="lingwistikis">lingwistikis</a> na <a href="pilosopi">pilosopi</a> na em i bin <a href="dokta%20save">dokta save</a> long <a href="lingwistikis">lingwistikis</a> (yia <a href="1995">1995</a>) (<a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "A Theory of Textual Reconstruction in Indo-European Linguistics").
Em i bos long <a href="historikal%20lingwistikis">historikal lingwistikis</a> long Pakulti bilong pilosopi long Zagreb. Em i memba long <a href="Akademi%20bilong%20Krowesia%20long%20save%20na%20tumbuna">Akademi bilong Krowesia long save na tumbuna</a> (<a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>: "The Croatian Academy of Sciences and Arts", <a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>: "Hrvatska akademija znanosti i umjetnosti"; yia <a href="2012">2012</a>).
Ol buk na pepa bilong em.
Em i raitim plani pepa long <a href="save">save</a> (<a href="Tok%20Krowesia">Tok Krowesia</a>, <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a>, <a href="Tok%20Rasian">Tok Rasian</a> na moa).
Em i tanim i bikpela samting pepa long <a href="Tok%20Latin">Tok Latin</a>, <a href="Tok%20Gris">Tok Gris</a>, <a href="Tok%20Lituwenia">Tok Lituwenia</a>, <a href="Tok%20Hitait">Tok Hitait</a>, <a href="Tok%20Aialan">Tok Aialan</a>, <a href="Tok%20Wels">Tok Wels</a>, <a href="Tok%20Inglis">Tok Inglis</a> na moa.
linked_text: Ranko Matasović (Mei 14, [[1968]]) em i man bilong [[Krowesia]]. Em i bikpela long [[histori]] long lingwistikis. Em i stadim [[Indo-Yuropien famili bilong tokples]] na em i lukluk histori bilong [[Tok Krowesia]], Baltik famili bilong tokples, Slavik famili bilong tokples, Keltik famili bilong tokples na mo tokples long Kokesen. Wok. Em i man bilong Zagreb. Em i bin stadim lingwistikis na [[pilosopi]] na em i bin dokta save long lingwistikis (yia [[1995]]) (Tok Inglis: "A Theory of Textual Reconstruction in Indo-European Linguistics"). Em i bos long historikal lingwistikis long Pakulti bilong pilosopi long Zagreb. Em i memba long Akademi bilong Krowesia long save na tumbuna (Tok Inglis: "The Croatian Academy of Sciences and Arts", [[Tok Krowesia]]: "Hrvatska akademija znanosti i umjetnosti"; yia 2012). Ol buk na pepa bilong em. Em i raitim plani pepa long save ([[Tok Krowesia]], Tok Inglis, Tok Rasian na moa). Em i tanim i bikpela samting pepa long [[Tok Latin]], [[Tok Gris]], [[Tok Lituwenia]], Tok Hitait, [[Tok Aialan]], Tok Wels, Tok Inglis na moa.

title: Novemba
text:
Novemba i <a href="mun">mun</a> namba wanpela ten wan bilong <a href="yia">yia</a> long <a href="Kalenda%20Pop%20Gregori">Kalenda Pop Gregori</a>. 
Dispela mun i gat 30 <a href="de">de</a> tasol. 
Nem Novemba i kam long Novem, i min "namba nain" long <a href="tok%20Latin">tok Latin</a>, olsem wanem dispela Mun i bin Mun namba nain long kalenda bilong ol <a href="Roma">Roma</a>, taim bipo tru. 
Long tok Inglis: "November".
linked_text: Novemba i [[mun]] namba wanpela ten wan bilong [[yia]] long Kalenda Pop Gregori.  Dispela mun i gat 30 [[de]] tasol.  Nem Novemba i kam long Novem, i min "namba nain" long [[tok Latin]], olsem wanem dispela Mun i bin Mun namba nain long kalenda bilong ol Roma, taim bipo tru.  Long tok Inglis: "November".

title: Haus bilong binen
text:
Ol binen ("Apis mellifera") i save wokim
haus bilong ol long wara
kain olsem gris kandel i stap aninit long
bel bilong ol.
Olgeta haus bilong binen i gat seip bilong
"hexagon, "em seip i gat 6-pela sait. Dispela i mekim na ol
binen inap yusim gut olgeta spes, wokim
haus long liklik hap wara i kain olsem
gris kandel, na tu, bungim planti hani
long wanpela liklik spes.
linked_text: Ol binen ("Apis mellifera") i save wokim haus bilong ol long wara kain olsem gris kandel i stap aninit long bel bilong ol. Olgeta haus bilong binen i gat seip bilong "hexagon, "em seip i gat 6-pela sait. Dispela i mekim na ol binen inap yusim gut olgeta spes, wokim haus long liklik hap wara i kain olsem gris kandel, na tu, bungim planti hani long wanpela liklik spes.

title: COVID-19 pandemic insait long Papua Niugini
text:
COVID-19 pandemic insait long Papua Niugini em i pat long <a href="COVID-19%20pandemic">pandemic</a> bilong <a href="SARS-CoV-2">SARS-CoV-2</a>. Em i bin namba wan keis long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a> long 20 Mas 2020. Papua Niugini em i bin kolim COVID-19 free long 4 Me 2020, tasol gavman em i bin painim narapela keis long 20 June. Tude Papua Niugini em i gat 453 ol keis, na 5 ol manmeri i dai pinis, na 232 ol manmeri i kisim mobeta.
Kirapim blong outbreak.
COVID-19 pandemic em i bin kirapim insait long Wuhan, Hubei Provins, <a href="Ol%20Manmeri%20Ripablik%20bilong%20Saina">Saina</a>, long Desemba 2019. Ya nupela virus na bin ripotim pastaim long World Health Organization antap long 31 Desemba 2019.
Em i bin namba wan keis long Papua Niugini blong man husat go long <a href="Spen">Spen</a>, na husat em i gat 45 krismas. Em i bin isolated insait long <a href="Lae">Lae</a>.

Papua Niugini em i bin kolim COVID-19 free long 4 Me 2020, tasol gavman em i bin painim narapela keis long 20 June. Tude Papua Niugini em i gat 453 ol keis, na 5 ol manmeri i dai pinis, na 232 ol manmeri i kisim mobeta. Kirapim blong outbreak. COVID-19 pandemic em i bin kirapim insait long Wuhan, Hubei Provins, Saina, long Desemba 2019. Ya nupela virus na bin ripotim pastaim long World Health Organization antap long 31 Desemba 2019. Em i bin namba wan keis long Papua Niugini blong man husat go long [[Spen]], na husat em i gat 45 krismas. Em i bin isolated insait long [[Lae]].

title: Tokples
text:
Tokples i tok bilong has ples bilong manmeri em i tokples bilong ol. Sampela save long tokples ol i kolim <a href="lingwistikis">lingwistikis</a>.
Tokples em i phenomenon long nature long manmeri; na moa tru taim manmeri lainim tokples long taim ol i bin pikinini. Tokples em i pattern long <a href="nois">nois</a> o gesture long symbols ol i yusim long komunikesen long narapela manmeri long namel long <a href="sens">sens</a>. Ol i gat tausens long tokples long <a href="graun">graun</a> na ol i sharim sampela propeti bilong olgeta.
Em i nogat klia idea long save wanem mekim sampela tokples o dialekt, tasol planti manmeri i toktok "tokples em i dialekt wantaim ami na nevi".
Sampela manmeri i mekim narapela tokples, wankain olsem <a href="Esperanto">Esperanto</a> na <a href="Klingon">Klingon</a>, tokples long progrem, na planti foamalisim long masematikis. 
Ol tokples i gat <a href="famili%20bilong%20tokples">famili bilong tokples</a>, o lain long em.

Tokples em i pattern long nois o gesture long symbols ol i yusim long komunikesen long narapela manmeri long namel long sens. Ol i gat tausens long tokples long graun na ol i sharim sampela propeti bilong olgeta. Em i nogat klia idea long save wanem mekim sampela tokples o dialekt, tasol planti manmeri i toktok "tokples em i dialekt wantaim ami na nevi". Sampela manmeri i mekim narapela tokples, wankain olsem [[Esperanto]] na Klingon, tokples long progrem, na planti foamalisim long masematikis.  Ol tokples i gat [[famili bilong tokples]], o lain long em.

title: Tagbanwa
text:
Tagbanwa o Tagbanwa em i manmeri husat i stap long <a href="Palawan">Palawan</a> long taim bipo. Em i stap long namel na not long Palawan. Sampla reasearch i bin painimaut olsem ol Tagbanwa manmeri i kamap long Tabon Man, olsem na em i nambawan manmeri husat i stap long Filipin na Palawan. Tagbanwa ya i gat braunpla skin na gras blong em i stret.
Tagbanwa manmeri i gat tupla bikpla hap. Hap ya i kamap long as ples blong em i stap we. Central Tagbanwa i stap long wes na is long namel blong Palawan. Em i stap long municiplaity blong Aborlan, Quezon na Puerto Princesa City.

title: Nonvailens
text:
Nonvailens, o ahimsa, i pasin bilong traim mekim senis long kantri o long gavman, tasol i no yusim vailens. Dispela i min olsem i no bagarapim narapela manmeri o ol samting bilong narapela manmeri.
<a href="Gandi">Gandi</a> i bin bikpela lida bilong muvmen igo long independens long India. Gandi i bin kamapim independens long India long yusim nonvailens.

title: Reptail
text:
Reptail (Reptilia) wanpela kalas bilong enimol. Ol i no nap palai na i no gat grass na ol i wokim kiau: pukpuk, snek, etc.

title: Georg Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel
text:
Georg Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel (<a href="Ogas%2027">Ogas 27</a>, <a href="1770">1770</a>–<a href="Novemba%2014">Novemba 14</a>, <a href="1831">1831</a>) i man bilong <a href="pilosopi">pilosopi</a> bilong kantri <a href="Siamani">Siamani</a>. 
Pilosopi long Hegel i as long <a href="Spinoza">Spinoza</a>, <a href="Kant">Kant</a>, <a href="Rousseau">Rousseau</a> na <a href="Revolution%20long%20Pranis">Revolution long Pranis</a>. Hegel tingting pilosopi bilong nau igat planti kontradikisen na tensen, wankain olsem <a href="subjekt">subjekt</a> na <a href="objekt">objekt</a> long <a href="save">save</a>, <a href="save">save</a> na <a href="lotu">lotu</a>, o <a href="enlaitenmen">enlaitenmen</a> na <a href="romantisisim">romantisisim</a>.
linked_text: Georg Wilhelm Friedrich Hegel (Ogas 27, 1770–Novemba 14, [[1831]]) i man bilong [[pilosopi]] bilong kantri [[Siamani]].  Pilosopi long Hegel i as long Spinoza, Kant, Rousseau na Revolution long Pranis. Hegel tingting pilosopi bilong nau igat planti kontradikisen na tensen, wankain olsem subjekt na objekt long save, save na [[lotu]], o enlaitenmen na romantisisim.

title: Kapitol
text: Kapitol em i asples bilong ol gavman. Tasol long sampela kantri, wanpela taun em i kapitol, na narapela em i bikpela taun tumas, olsem <a href="Yunaitet%20Stet">Amerika</a>: <a href="Washington">Washington</a> em i kapitol, tasol <a href="New%20York">New York</a> em i bikpela taun tumas.

title: Wol
text:
"Dispela pes i toktok long <a href="Jiograpi">Jiograpi</a> bilong Graun. Sapos you laik lukluk long pes bilong <a href="Estronomi">Estronomi</a> bilong Graun tasol, lukim <a href="Giraun">Giraun</a>."
Wol em i ples we olgeta man o meri i stap. Nau samting olsem 7000 milien manmeri i stap long wol. 
Ol i kolim wol <a href="Graun">Graun</a> tu. Graun i planet bilong yumi. Wol i gat planti <a href="kantri">kantri</a> long faifpela <a href="kontinen">kontinen</a> na planti <a href="solwara">solwara</a>. 
Nem bilong save bilong <a href="Wol">Wol</a> na olgeta kain ples na graun emi <a href="Save%20long%20giraun">Save long giraun</a> ().
linked_text: "Dispela pes i toktok long Jiograpi bilong Graun. Sapos you laik lukluk long pes bilong [[Estronomi]] bilong Graun tasol, lukim [[Giraun]]." title: Maun Hagen
text:
Maun Hagen o Hagen em i <a href="kapitol">kapitol</a> na taun bikpela tumas bilong <a href="Westen%20Hailans">Westen Hailans</a> provins long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">Papua Niugini</a>. Em i namba tri taun long Papua Niugini; <a href="Pot%20Mosbi">Pot Mosbi</a> na <a href="Lae">Lae</a> i bikpela moa long em. Hagen i kisim nem long <a href="Maun%20Hagen%20%28maunten%29">Maun Hagen</a>, wanpela bikpela maunten i stap klostu long taun.
Histori.
Long yia <a href="1933">1933</a>, Mick Leahy na brata bilong em Dan Leahy, tupela i kisim balus na tupela i painim ples <a href="Wagi%20Vali">Wagi Vali</a>. Tupela painem ples we planti manmeri i stap.
Liklik taim bihain, tupela i kisim sampela ofisa (wanpela ofisa husat i kamap wantaim tupela brata, nem bilong em Jim Taylor), na ol i kamap olsem nambawan waitman long wokabout i go long Maun Hagen. Ol i wokim wanpela liklik ples balus tu.
Trenspot.
Maun Hagen en i gat wanpela bikpela ples balus, nem bilong em i Kagamuga ples balus. Maun Hagen tu i stap long <a href="Hailans%20Haiwe">Hailans Haiwe</a>, rot we manmeri i ken kamap long <a href="Lae">Lae</a> na <a href="Madang">Madang</a>. Hailans Haiwe em i wanpela rot i gat sel. <a href="Westen%20Hailans">Westen Hailans</a> i gat sampela mo rot tu, tasol planti i no gat sel.
linked_text: Maun Hagen o Hagen em i [[kapitol]] na taun bikpela tumas bilong [[Westen Hailans]] provins long [[Papua Niugini]]. Em i namba tri taun long Papua Niugini; [[Pot Mosbi]] na [[Lae]] i bikpela moa long em. Hagen i kisim nem long [[Maun Hagen]], wanpela bikpela maunten i stap klostu long taun. Histori. Long yia [[1933]], Mick Leahy na brata bilong em Dan Leahy, tupela i kisim balus na tupela i painim ples Wagi Vali. Tupela painem ples we planti manmeri i stap. Liklik taim bihain, tupela i kisim sampela ofisa (wanpela ofisa husat i kamap wantaim tupela brata, nem bilong em Jim Taylor), na ol i kamap olsem nambawan waitman long wokabout i go long [[Maun Hagen]]. [[Ol]] i wokim wanpela liklik ples balus tu. Trenspot. Maun Hagen en i gat wanpela bikpela ples balus, nem bilong em i Kagamuga ples balus. Maun Hagen tu i stap long Hailans Haiwe, rot we manmeri i ken kamap long [[Lae]] na Madang. Hailans Haiwe em i wanpela rot i gat sel. [[Westen Hailans]] i gat sampela mo rot tu, tasol planti i no gat sel.

title: St. Peter's College, Auckland
text:
St. Peter’s College emi i wanpela bikpela Katolic sekendary skul bilong ol mangi (pikinini man) tasol, na em i stap long sentrol Auckland citi. Dispela skul emi stap namel tru long Auckland citi long New Zealand. 
Bigpela bilong em i winim olgeta Katolik sekendari skul long New Zealand. Ol Kristian Brothers ol bin kamapim dispela skul long yia 1939, tasol long yia 2008 ol man we ol i no missionary ol lukautim.
1200 mangi long ol kain kain kantri ol i skul long dispela skul.
Dispela skul em i givim ol bikpela mangi, National Certificate of Education Achievement assessment system, ol i kolim long NCEA na Cambridge International Examinations ol I kolim long CIE. 
Skul em i save enrolim seven pela ten (70) student long overseas. Ol big name man we ol I bing skul long dispela skul em Sir Michael Fay (em I wanpela bisines man na man bilong drivim ol liklik boat wantaim sel) na Sam Hunt (em man bilong raitim poetry).
Website bilong College: <a href="http%3A//www.st-peters.school.nz/">www.st-peters.school.nz</a>
Moto bilong skul: To Love and To Share (Amare et Servire)
